\id JHN Quechua de Margos-Yarowilca-Lauricocha, Huánuco 
\h SAN JUAN 
\toc1 SAN JUAN Jesucristupita escribishgan 
\toc2 SAN JUAN 
\toc3 Jn. 
\mt1 SAN JUAN 
\mt2 Jesucristupita escribishgan 
\ip Apóstol Juanmi cay libruta escribergan. Payga puntata Juan Bautistapa discïpulunmi cargan (1.35-42). Tsaypitaragmi Jesuspa discïpulun cargan. Jesuswan purirmi rurashgancunata ricargan y yachatsishgantapis mayargan. Tsaynog purirmi tantyargan salvamänantsipag Jesucristuta Tayta Diosnintsi cachamushganta. 
\ip Juanga cay libruta escribergan salvamänantsipag Jesucristo shamushganta nogantsipis musyanantsipagmi. Tsaynogpis cay libruta escribergan Jesucristuman yäracur gloriacho cushishgala imayyagpis cawanantsipag cashganta musyanantsipagmi (20.31). 
\c 1  
\s1 Dios caycar Jesucristo cay patsaman shamushgan 
\p  
\v 1-2 Imapis manarag captinmi Jesucristo mayna caycargan. Tayta Dioswanmi pay caycargan. Payga Diosnintsimi. 
\p  
\v 3 Paywanmi Tayta Dios camargan lapan imaycatapis.  
\v 4 Paymi cay patsacho cagtaga lapantapis cawayta gon. Tsaynog cawayta gon runacuna Tayta Dios munashgannog cawapäcunanpagmi.  
\v 5 Tsaynog captinpis runacuna jutsalancho cawarmi tsacäpacushganog carcaycan. Tsaymi mana tantyantsu Tayta Diosnintsi munashgannog cawananpag. Tsaynog captinmi Jesucristo runacunata tantyatsin jutsa ruraycunata cacharir Tayta Dios munashgannogna cawapäcunanpag. 
\p  
\v 6-7 Jesucristuta runacuna chasquicunanpagmi Juan Bautista wilacorgan. Tsaynog wilacunanpagmi Tayta Dios payta acrargan.  
\v 8 Shumag wilacuptinmi runacuna yarpapäcorgan Juan Bautista salvacog Jesucristo cashganta. Tsaynog yarpaptinpis manami Jesucristutsu payga cargan, sinöga Jesucristuta chasquicärinanpag wilacoglami. 
\p  
\v 9 Jesucristoga atsquinogmi caycan. Tsaymi cay patsaman shamorgan runacunapag atsquinog cananpag.  
\v 10-11 Cay patsaman shamuptinpis runacuna manami tantyargantsu Jesucristoga Tayta Diospa naupanpita shamushganta. Tsaynogpis payta manami chasquicärergantsu, Tayta Dioswan cay patsata camashga caycaptinpis.  
\v 12 Tsaynog captinpis Jesucristuta chasquicogcunami itsanga Tayta Diosnintsipa wamrancunana carcaycan.  
\v 13 Tsaynog niycaptenga manami mamanpita yurishganpitatsu Tayta Diospa wamrancuna carcaycan, sinöga Jesucristuta chasquicushganpitami. 
\p  
\v 14 Tayta Dioswan caycashganpita cay patsacho runanog yurishpanmi Jesucristoga nogacunawan purergan. Paywan purirmi ricapäcorgä cuyacog cashganta. Tsaynogpis mayapäcorgä Diospa wilacuyninta yachatsishganta. Payga Tayta Diospa japalan cuyay tsurinmi. Tsaymi payta ricar quiquin Tayta Diosta ricagnogna capäcorgä.  
\v 15 Paypitami Juan Bautista caynog nir wilacorgan: “Jesucristoga nogapita más munayniyogmi caycan. Payga manaragpis yuriptë maynami caycarganna.” 
\p  
\v 16-17 Moisesga Tayta Diospa mandamientuncunalatami tantyatsergan. Jesucristumi itsanga cuyamashpantsi tantyatsimantsi Tayta Dios salvamänantsipag cag mushog wilacuyninta.  
\v 18 Manami pipis Tayta Diosta ricashgatsu. Paytaga ricashga japalan cuyay tsurin Jesucristulami. Tsaymi pay cagpita shamushga car tantyatsimashcantsi Tayta Dios imanog cashgantapis. 
\s1 Juan Bautista wilacushgan 
\r (Mateo 3.1-12; Marcos 1.2-8; Lucas 3.15-17) 
\p  
\v 19 Jordán mayucho Juan Bautista runacunata bautizaycaptinmi Jerusalenpita autoridäcuna Juan cagman cachargan cüracunata y Leví casta runacunata. Paycunata cachargan Cristo cashganta o juc cashgantapis tapumunanpag.  
\v 20 Tsay runacuna tapuptinmi Juan caynog nergan: “Nogaga manami Cristutsu cä.” 
\p  
\v 21 Tsaynog niptinmi yapay taporgan: “Tsauraga ¿pitag caycanqui? ¿Tayta Diospa unay wilacognin Eliascu?”\f + \fr 1:21 \ft Malaquías 4.5-6 escribishgancho Tayta Dios nergan Jesucristo manarag shamuptin unay wilacognin Elías cutimunanpag cashganta. Eliaspita y Juan Bautistapita masta musyanayquipag liyinqui San Mateo 17.10-13; San Lucas 1.17.\f* 
\p Tsaymi Juan Bautista nergan: “Manami Eliastsu caycä.” 
\p Tsaymi yapay taporgan: “Tsauraga ¿Moisés nishgannog shamunanpag cag wilacog profëtacu caycanqui?”\f + \fr 1:21 \ft Moisés nishgannog shamunanpag cag profëtapita musyanayquipag liyinqui Deuteronomio 18.15-19.\f* 
\p Niptinmi nergan: “Manami paytsu cä.” 
\p  
\v 22 Tsaynog niptinmi nipäcorgan: “Tsauraga ¿pitag canqui? Autoridäcunata wilanäpag pï cashgayquitapis wilapäcamay.” 
\p  
\v 23 Tsauraga Juan caynog nergan: “Nogaga Isaías escribishgannoglami Tayta Diospa wilacognin caycä. Tsaymi chunyag jircaman shamog runacunata wilapaycä jutsancunata cacharir Cristo shamuptin chasquicärinanpag.”\x + \xo 1:23 \xt Isaías 40.3\x* 
\p  
\v 24 Juanta tapunanpag autoridä cachashgan runacunaga waquin cargan fariseo runacunami. Paycunami Juanta taporgan caynog nir:  
\v 25 “Tsauraga ni Cristo, ni Elías, ni Moisés escribishgannog shamunanpag caycag profëtapis mana caycarga ¿imanirtag runacunata bautizaycanqui?” 
\p  
\v 26-27 Tsaynog tapuptin Juan nergan: “Nogaga yaculawanmi bautizaycä. Itsanga jucragmi shamonga nogapita más munayniyog. Nogaga manami paynog munayniyogtsu caycä. Cay patsachöna caycaptinpis runacuna manami tantyacuntsu salvamagnintsi Cristo cashganta.” 
\p  
\v 28 Tsaynöga Juanta tapupäcorgan Jordán mayu tsimpan Betaniachömi. Tsaychömi runacunata Juan bautizaycargan. 
\s1 Jesucristo aywaycämogta Juan Bautista ricashgan 
\p  
\v 29 Tsaypita wara junag Jesús aywaycämogta ricarmi Juan Bautista caynog nergan: “¡Ricapäcuy Tayta Dios cachamushgan runa aywaycämogta! Pascua aniversariucho carnishta wanutsipäcushgannogmi pay wanonga runacuna jutsa rurashgancunapita perdonashga cananpag.  
\v 30 Nogapita más munayniyog cashganta y manaragpis yuriptë pay mayna caycashgantami noga wilacö. 
\p  
\v 31 “Naupataga manami musyargätsu Tayta Dios cachamushgan Cristo pï runa cashgantapis. Pï cashganta manarag musyarpis nogaga runacunata bautizaycashcä shamuptin payta chasquicärinanpagmi.  
\v 32-33 Jesucristo pï cashgantapis musyanäpagmi Tayta Dios caynog nimargan: ‘Bautizarcuptiqui maygan runapa jananman Santu Espíritu palomanog rataptinmi musyanquipag tsay runa Jesucristo cashganta. Paymi munayniyog caycan Santu Espirituwan runacunata bautizananpag.’  
\v 34 Tsay nimashgannoglami Jesusta bautizarcuptë paypa jananman Santu Espíritu palomanog rataycagta ricargä. Tsaymi gamcunata wilapä Tayta Diosnintsipa tsurin pay cashganta.” 
\s1 Punta cag discïpuluncunata Jesucristo acrashgan 
\p  
\v 35-36 Tsaypita wara junag ishcay discïpuluncunawan caycarmi Juan Bautista ricargan Jesús pasaycagta. Payta ricarmi Juan Bautista caynog nergan: “¡Ricapäcuy! ¡Salvamagnintsi Cristo pasaycan!” 
\p  
\v 37 Tsaynog niptinmi Jesuspa guepanpa tsay ishcay discïpulucuna aywapäcorgan.  
\v 38 Ticraycamushganchömi Jesús ricargan guepanpa paycuna aywaycagta. Tsaymi taporgan: “¿Maypatag aywarcaycanqui?” 
\p Niptinmi nipäcorgan: “Gam cagmanmi aywaycämorgä, rabí. ¿Maychötag posädaraycanqui?” (Rabí ninanga yachatsicog ninanmi.) 
\p  
\v 39 Tsaymi Jesús: “Acu, posädacushgä wayita reguitsishayqui” nergan. 
\p Tsaymi reguitsergan maycho posädarashgantapis. Tardina captinnami Jesuswan quëdacorgan posädacushgan cagcho. 
\p  
\v 40 Tsay ishcay discïpuluncuna jucag cargan Simón Pedrupa wauguin Andresmi.  
\v 41 Tsauraga jinan hörami Andrés aywargan wauguin Simón cagman. Chayaycurmi wilargan caynog nir: “¡Tincupäcushcä Tayta Dios cachamushgan Cristuwanmi!” 
\p  
\v 42 Nircurnami Jesús cagman pushargan. Chayaycuptinnami Simonta ricaycur Jesús caynog nergan: “Jonaspa tsurin Simón, cananpitaga Pedrunami jutiqui canga.” 
\s1 Felipita y Natanaelta discïpulun cananpag Jesucristo acrashgan 
\p  
\v 43 Tsaypita wara junag Galilea provinciapa Jesús aywananpagna caycarmi tincorgan Felipiwan. Tsaymi payta nergan: “Discïpulö canayquipag nogawan aywashun.” 
\p  
\v 44 Felipega cargan Betsaida marcapitami. Andreswan Pedrupis tsay marcalapitami cargan.  
\v 45 Discïpulun cananpag Jesús niptinmi Felipe aywargan Natanaelta caynog wilananpag: “¡Tayta Dios cachamushgan Cristuwanmi tincupäcushcä! ¡Payga Josëpa tsurin Nazaret marcapita Jesusmi! ¿Yarpanquicu Moisés y waquin profëtacuna pay shamur salvamänantsipag escribishganta? ¡Paywanmi tincupäcushcä!” 
\p  
\v 46 Niptinmi Natanael nergan: “¿Imanogpatag Nazaret marcapita Tayta Dios cachamushgan Cristo canman?” 
\p Tsaynog niptinmi Felipe nergan: “Acu aywashun ricanayquipag.” 
\p  
\v 47 Tsaymi Natanael aywaycämogta ricar runacunata Jesús nergan: “Tagay aywaycämog runaga ali runami. Payga rasun caglata imatapis parlan.” 
\p  
\v 48 Tsay nishganta mayashpanmi Natanael taporgan: “¿Imanogpatag musyanqui ali runa cashgäta?” 
\p Tsauraga Jesús nergan: “Manami ali runa cashgalayquitatsu musyä, sinöga maycho cashgayquitapis musyämi. Tsaymi Felipe manarag gayashuptiquipis nogaga ricashcä hïgus yöra chaquincho jamaraycashgayquita.” 
\p  
\v 49 Tsaynog niptinmi Natanael nergan: “¡Tayta Diospa tsurinmi gam caycanqui, tayta! ¡Tsaynogpis Israel runacunapa mandagnin reymi caycanqui!” 
\p  
\v 50 Tsaynog niptinmi Jesús nergan: “¿Hïgus yöra chaquincho jamaraycashgayquita ricashgäta nishgaläpitacu tsaynog nimanqui? Cananpitaga milagrucunata rurashgätapis ricanquipagmi.” 
\p  
\v 51 Tsauraga tsaycho caycag runacunata Jesús caynog nergan: “Angilcuna ciëlupita uraycämogta y witsaycagta sueñuynincho ricarmi Jacob tantyargan Tayta Dios yanapaycashganta.\f + \fr 1:51 \ft Tsaypita masta musyanayquipag liyinqui Génesis 28.10-17.\f* Tsayta ricar Jacob tantyashgannogmi gamcunapis tantyanquipag Tayta Dios \nd nogata\nd* yanapaycämashganta.” 
\c 2  
\s1 Yacuta vïnuman Jesucristo ticratsishgan 
\p  
\v 1 Tsaypita quimsa junagtanami casaray fiesta cargan Galilea provinciacho cag Caná marcacho. Tsay fiestachömi caycargan Jesuspa mamanpis.  
\v 2 Tsay fiestamanmi Jesusta y discïpuluncunatapis gayatsergan.  
\v 3 Manarag fiesta ushacaptinmi vïnu ushacäcorgan. Tsauraga Jesusta maman caynog nergan: “Vïnu ushacashganami. ¿Maypitarag canan vïnuta jorgamonga?” 
\p  
\v 4 Tsaynog niptin mamanta Jesús nergan: “Manami hörä chämunragtsu munashgayquinog milagruta ruranäpag, mamä.” 
\p  
\v 5 Tsaynog niptinpis serviciucunata maman caynog nergan: “Imata ruranayquipag Jesús nishuptiquega cäsucärinqui.” 
\p  
\v 6 Tsaychömi caycargan rumipita rurashga yacuynag sogta urpucuna. Tsay urpucunamanmi yacuta winapäcog costumbrin cashgannog maquinta maylacärinanpag. Waquin urpucunamanmi yaycog ganchis chunca (70) litro yacu y waquinmannami yaycog pitsga chunca (50) litro yacu.  
\v 7 Tsauraga serviciucunata Jesús caynog nergan: “Tsay urpucunaman yacuta juntagpag winapäcuy.” 
\p Tsaymi yacuta winapäcorgan urpucunaman juntashganyag.  
\v 8 Juntarcuptinnami Jesús nergan: “Ichiclata chagarcur apay mayor servicio yawananpag.” 
\p Jesús nishgannog rurapäcuptinmi tsay yacu ticrargan vïnuman.  
\v 9 Tsaymi apapashgan vïnuta yawarcorgan mayor servicio. Itsanga manami musyargantsu maypita apashgantapis. Yanapag cag serviciucunalami musyargan yacupita vïnuman Jesús ticratsishganta. Tsay vïnuta yawarcurnami casarag mözuta gayaycur caynog nergan:  
\v 10 “¡Tsayrag apamushgan vïnoga waquin vïnupitapis más alimi caycan! ¿Maychötag tsay vïnutaga tarishcanqui? Waquin runacunaga fiesta galaycunalanchömi alinnin cag vïnuta sirvicun. Gammi itsanga fiesta ushananchörag más alinnin cag vïnuta sirvicuycanqui.” 
\p  
\v 11 Tsaynogmi Galileacho cag Caná marcacho Jesús rurargan punta cag milagruta. Munayniyog cashganta ricarmi discïpuluncuna tantyapäcorgan Tayta Dios cachamushgan Cristo cashganta. 
\p  
\v 12 Tsaypitanami mamanwan, wauguincunawan y discïpuluncunawanpis Jesús aywargan Capernaum marcaman. Tsaychömi goyargan juc ishcay junag. 
\s1 Templo patiucho ranticogcunata Jesucristo gargushgan 
\r (Mateo 21.12-13; Marcos 11.15-17; Lucas 19.45-46) 
\p  
\v 13 Pascua aniversario galaycunanpagna caycaptinmi Jesús aywargan Jerusalén marcaman.  
\v 14 Chayashpannami templo patiucho tarergan atsca runacuna ranticurcaycagta. Tsaychömi ranticuycargan törucunata, uyshacunata y palomacunatapis. Tsaynogpis tarergan guellay ranticogcunata.\f + \fr 2:14 \ft Jesús cawanan witsanmi Roma runacunapa guellayninta Israel runacuna tsararag imatapis rantinanpag. Tayta Diosnintsipag ofrendata apananpagmi itsanga templuman apananpag cag guellaytarag rantipäcog.\f* 
\v 15 Tsaynog ranticuycagta tariycushpanmi sumbadorta rurarcur uyshantinta wäcantinta Jesús gargorgan templo patiupita. Guellayta ranticogcunapa mësancunatapis ticrar ushargan guellaynincunatapis mashtariycushpan.  
\v 16 Tsaynog gargurmi paloma ranticogcunatapis caynog nergan: “¡Caycunata jorgapäcuy! Taytäta adoracuna wayichöga ¿imanirtag mercädo captinnogpis caycho ranticurcaycanqui?” 
\p  
\v 17 Jesús tsaynog ruraptinmi discïpuluncuna tantyapäcorgan Tayta Diospa palabrancho escribiraycashgannogla ruraycashganta. Tsay escribirashganga caynogmi niycan: “Templuchöga Tayta Diosta adorapäcunalantami munä.”\x + \xo 2:17 \xt Salmo 69.9\x* 
\p  
\v 18 Tsaynog garguptinmi Israel runacunapa autoridänincuna payta nipäcorgan: “¿Ima munayniquiwantag ranticogcunata gargushcanqui? Mä milagruta ruray munayniyog cashgayquita musyapäcunäpag.” 
\p  
\v 19 Tsaynog niptinmi Jesús caynog nergan: “Milagruta ricayta munarga cay templuta juchutsipäcuy. Juchutsiptiquega quimsa junaglatami noga sharcatsishagpag.” 
\p  
\v 20 Tsaynog niptinmi autoridäcuna nipäcorgan: “Cay templuta sharcatsipäcorgan chuscu chunca sogta (46) watatami. ¿Imanogpatag canan gam quimsa junaglata yapay sharcaratsinquiman?” 
\p  
\v 21 Tsaynog nir Jesús manami templuta yapay sharcatsinanpagtsu nergan, sinöga quiquin wanushganpita quimsa junagta cawarimunanpag cashgantami niycargan. Tsaymi autoridäcuna Jesús imapita parlaycashgantapis mana tantyapäcorgantsu.  
\v 22 Discïpuluncunapis manami juclaga tantyapäcorgantsu. Jesús wanushganpita cawarimushganta ricarragmi tantyapäcorgan templuman jitaycular quiquinpag parlashganta. Tsaynogpami musyapäcorgan Tayta Diosnintsipa palabrancho Jesuspita escribiraycashgan y Jesús nishgancunapis rasun cag cashganta. 
\s1 Runacuna imata yarpashgantapis Jesucristo musyashgan 
\p  
\v 23 Pascua aniversariucho atsca runacunami ricapäcorgan milagrucunata Jesús ruraycashganta. Tsaynogpami tantyapäcorgan Tayta Dios cachamushgan Cristo cashganta.  
\v 24 Tsaynog tantyacuptinpis Jesús musyarganmi payman mana yäracuycashganta.  
\v 25 Mana wilaptinpis payga musyarganmi runacuna imata yarpashgantapis. 
\c 3  
\s1 Nicodemuwan Jesucristo parlashgan 
\p  
\v 1 Juc fariseo runami cargan Nicodemo jutiyog. Payga Israel runacunapa autoridäninmi cargan.  
\v 2 Paymi tsacaylapa Jesús cagman aywargan parlananpag. Chayaycurmi caynog nergan: “Milagrucunata rurashgayquita musyarmi tantyapäcö Tayta Dios yanapaycäshushgayquita, tayta. Tsaymi musyapäcö nogacunata yachatsimänayquipag cachamushushgayquita.” 
\p  
\v 3 Tsauraga Jesús caynog nergan: “Runacuna Tayta Diospa naupanman chayananpäga yapayragmi yurinman. Yapay mana yurerga manami pipis gloriaman chayangapagtsu.” 
\p  
\v 4 Tsauraga Nicodemo caynog taporgan: “¿Imanogpatag runacuna yapay yurinman yurishgana caycarga? ¿Cutinmantsurag mamanpa pachanman yapay yurinanpag?” 
\p  
\v 5 Tsauraga Jesús caynog nergan: “Manami runacuna mamanpa pachanman cutinanpagtsu niycä, sinöga Santu Espiritupa munayninwan yapay yurinanpagmi. Pipis yacuwan\f + \fr 3:5 \ft Santu Espirituta yacuman tincutsishganta musyanayquipag liyinqui Ezequiel 36.25-27.\f* y Santu Espiritupa munayninwan yapay mana yurerga manami Tayta Diospa naupanman chayangapagtsu.  
\v 6 Manami pipis mamanpita yurishgalanpitatsu salvashga canga, sinöga Santu Espiritupa munayninwan yurishganpitaragmi.  
\v 7 Gloriaman chayananpag lapan runa yapayragmi yurinman niptë ama mantsacaytsu.  
\v 8 Wayrämogta mayarpis runacuna manami musyantsu maypita wayra shamushganta ni maypa aywashgantapis. Tsaynoglami runacuna mana tantyapäcuntsu yapay yurishganog cananpag Santu Espíritu imata rurashgantapis.” 
\p  
\v 9 Tsaynog niptinmi Nicodemo nergan: “Nogaläpis tsaytaga manami tantyätsu, tayta.” 
\p  
\v 10 Tsaynog niptinmi Jesús caynog nergan: “Israel runacunapa yachatsegnin caycar ¿manacu tsayta tantyanqui?  
\v 11 Tsay nishgäcunata mana tantyaptiquipis nogaga gamta wilapaycä musyashgätami. Tsaynog captinpis gamcuna manami criyipäcunquitsu nishgäta.  
\v 12 Runacuna yapay yurishganog cananpag nishgäta mana criyiycarga ¿imanogpatag criyipäcunquiman masta niptëpis? 
\p  
\v 13 “Manami pipis gloriaman aywarcur cutimushgatsu tsaycho imanog cashgantapis runacunata wilananpag. \nd Nogami\nd* itsanga gloriapita cay patsaman shamushcä. Tsaymi rasun cagta runacunata wilapä.  
\v 14-15 Pipis nogata chasquicamagcunaga gloriacho cushishgami imayyagpis cawangapag. Tsaynog cawananpäga puntata \nd noga\nd* wanushagragmi. Chunyag tsaqui jircacho culebra picashganpita runacuna aliyänanpag broncipita rurashga culebrata Moisés shawashgannogmi nogapis cruzcho wanushag chasquicamag runacuna salvacärinanpag.”\f + \fr 3:14-15 \ft Tayta Dios mandaptinmi broncipita culebrata Moisés rurargan. Nircurmi guerupa puntanman watarcur jawergan runacuna ricananpag. Tsayta ricagcunatami Tayta Diosnintsi aliyätsergan culebra picashganpita. Masta musyanayquipag liyinqui Números 21.4-9.\f* 
\s1 Runacunata Tayta Dios cuyapashgan 
\p  
\v 16 Runacunata cuyashpanmi Tayta Dios cachamorgan cuyay tsurinta. Tsaynogpami pipis Tayta Diospa tsurinta chasquicur payman yäracog cäga infiernuman manana gaycushgatsu canga, sinöga gloriamanmi chayanga imayyagpis tsaycho cawananpag.  
\v 17-18 Tayta Diosnintsega tsurinta cachamorgan payman yäracogcunata salvananpagmi. Tsaymi Tayta Diospa tsurinman yäracog cäga gloriaman chayangapag. Mana yäracog cagmi itsanga infiernuman gaycushga cangapag.  
\v 19-20 Paycunaga jutsa rurashgancunata cachariyta manami munantsu. Tsaymi Tayta Diospa tsurin cay patsaman shamushga captinpis payta mana chasquicärintsu.  
\v 21 Tayta Diospa tsurinta chasquicog cagmi itsanga jutsa ruraycunata cacharin. Tsaynog cacharinanpäga Tayta Diosnintsimi payta yanapan. 
\s1 Jesucristo shamunanpag cashganta Juan Bautista wilacushgan 
\p  
\v 22 Tsaypitanami Jesuswan discïpuluncuna aywapäcorgan Judea provinciaman. Tsaychömi runacunata bautizapäcorgan.  
\v 23 Juan Bautistanami bautizaycargan Enón nishgan ragracho, tsaycho atsca yacu captin. Enón cargan Salim marca cercanchömi. Tsaycho bautizaycashganta musyarmi waquin runacunaga tsayman aywargan bautizacärinanpag.  
\v 24 Tsay witsanga Juan manaragmi carcilcho wichgararganragtsu. 
\p  
\v 25 Tsaychömi Israel runacunapa juc ishcay autoridänincuna Juan Bautistapa discïpuluncunata nergan: “Jesús bautizashganmi más ali caycan Juan bautizashganpitaga.”  
\v 26 Tsaynog niptinmi discïpuluncuna Juanta caynog nipäcorgan: “Tayta, ¿yarpanquicu Jordán tsimpancho caycar juc runapita wilapämashgayquita? Cananga paymannami lapan runacuna aywarcaycan bautizacärinanpag.” 
\p  
\v 27 Tsaynog nipäcuptinmi Juan caynog nergan: “Nogapita más munayniyog captinmi runacuna payman aywarcaycan.  
\v 28 Gamcunata nishgänogpis manami Tayta Dios cachamushgan Cristutsu nogaga caycä. Tsaypa trucanga Cristuta runacuna chasquicunanpag wilacunaläpagmi Tayta Dios cachamashga.  
\v 29 Jipashwan juc mözu casaraptin amïgun cushicushgannoglami nogapis cushicö runacuna Jesucristumanna aywapäcuptin.  
\v 30 Nogaman shapäcamunanpa trucanga más alimi caycan paymanna runacuna aywaptin. 
\p  
\v 31 “Gloriapita shamushga carmi Jesucristo musyan tsaycho imanog cashgantapis. Nogaga cay patsalapita carmi mana paynöga musyätsu. Tsaymi tantyashgaläta wilacö.  
\v 32 Jesucristumi itsanga wilacuycan gloriacho ricashgancunata y mayashgancunatapis. Tsaynog wilacuptinpis mana chasquicogcunaga manami tantyapäcuntsu rasun cagta wilacushganta.  
\v 33-34 Chasquicogcunami itsanga tantyapäcun rasun cagta wilacuycashganta. Jesucristoga tsaynog wilacuycan Tayta Diosnintsipita shamushga carmi. Tsaynog wilacunanpäga Santu Espiritumi payta yanapaycan. Tsaymi pay wilacushgannöga pipis mana wilacuntsu. 
\p  
\v 35 “Tsurinta cuyarmi Tayta Diosnintsi lapantapis paypa munayninman cachaycushga.  
\v 36 Tsaymi Diospa tsurin Jesucristuta chasquicog cagtaga gloriaman shuntanga tsaycho imayyagpis cushishga cawananpag. Payta mana chasquicog cagtami itsanga Tayta Diosnintsi rabiashpan infiernuman gayconga imayyagpis tsaycho nacananpag.” 
\c 4  
\s1 Samaria warmiwan Jesucristo parlashgan 
\p  
\v 1 Fariseo runacunami musyapäcorgan Juan Bautista bautizashganpita más atsca runacunata Jesús bautizaycashganta.  
\v 2-3 Fariseo runacuna tsaynog musyashganta tantyarmi Jesuswan discïpuluncuna cutergan Judea provinciapita Galilea provinciaman. Itsanga manami quiquintsu Jesús bautizargan, sinöga discïpuluncunami runacunata bautizargan. 
\p  
\v 4 Galilea provinciaman chayapäcunanpäga Samaria provinciaparagmi pasapäcorgan.  
\v 5 Tsaypa pasarmi Samariacho cag Sicar nishgan marca naupanman chayapäcorgan. Tsaychömi Jacobpa chacran cargan. Tsay chacratami tsurin Josëta unay goycorgan.  
\v 6 Tsay chacrachömi cargan Jacob yacuta jorgunanpag uchcutsishgan pözu. Tsay pözu cagman chayaycurmi Jesús uticashga jamaycorgan. Tsay höra cargan pulan junagnognami.  
\v 7-8 Tsaycho Jesús jamapashganyagmi discïpuluncuna micuyta ranteg marcapa aywapäcorgan. Micuyta ranteg aywashganyagmi Jesús jamaraycashgan cagman Samaria warmi chayargan yacucog. Tsaymi yacunashpan yacuta Jesús manacorgan tsay warmita. 
\p  
\v 9 Tsay witsanga Samaria runacunawan Israel runacuna contra contra ricanacorgan. Tsaymi yacuta manacuptin tsay warmi caynog nergan Jesusta: “Israel runa caycarga ¿imanirtag yacuta manacamanqui Samaria warmi cashgäta musyaycar?” 
\p  
\v 10 Tsauraga Jesús caynog nergan: “Tayta Diosnintsipa palabranta tantyar y noga pï cashgätapis musyarga gampis yacuta manacamanquimanmi. Manacamaptiquega cawatsicog yacutami camaripäshayqui.” 
\p  
\v 11 Tsauraga tsay warmi nergan: “Yacoga rurichöragmi caycan. Jorgunayquipag imayquipis mana caycaptenga ¿imanogpatag jorgamunquiman cawatsicog yacuta camaripämänayquipäga?  
\v 12 Jacobmi cay pözuta unay uchcutsergan. Cay pözupitami yacuta upupäcorgan uywancunapis, tsurincunapis y quiquinpis. Paypis cay pözupitarag yacuta jorgamushga caycaptenga gam ¿maypitatag tsay yacuta jorgamunquiman?” 
\p  
\v 13 Tsaynog niptinmi Jesús nergan: “Cay pözupita yacuta upog cäga yapaypis yacunangapagmi.  
\v 14 Noga camaripashgä yacuta upog cagmi itsanga imaypis manana yacunangapagnatsu. Paycunaga Tayta Diospa naupanchömi imayyagpis cawangapag.” 
\p  
\v 15 Tsauraga Jesusta tsay warmi caynog nergan: “Imaypis mana yacunänäpag ni cay pözumanpis yacucog manana cutiycämunäpag tsay yacuta camaripaycalämay, tayta.” 
\p  
\v 16 Tsaymi Jesús nergan: “Ayway runayquita pushamunayquipag.” 
\p  
\v 17-18 Tsauraga tsay warmi nergan: “Manami runä cantsu, tayta.” 
\p Tsaynog niptinmi Jesús nergan: “Rasun cagtami gam nimashcanqui. Gamga pitsga runawannami tashcanqui. Canan taycashgayqui runapis puripänacushgayqui runalami caycan.” 
\p  
\v 19 Tsaynog niptin tsay warmi nergan: “Diospa profëtan imachari gam caycanqui, tayta.  
\v 20 Nogacunapa auquilöcunaga tagay jircachömi Tayta Diosta adorapäcog. Gamcunaga, Israel runacuna carmi, ‘Jerusalenchörag Tayta Diosta adorashun’ nircaycanqui.” 
\p  
\v 21 Tsaynog niptinmi Jesús caynog nergan: “Tagay jircaman mana aywaypa ni Jerusalenmanpis mana aywaypa Tayta Diosta adoranayquipag cag höra chaycämunnami.  
\v 22 Tayta Diosta adorarpis Samariapita cashpayquimi gamcuna shumag mana musyanquitsu Tayta Diospa wilacuyninta. Tayta Dios cachamushgan salvacog runa Israel runa captinmi nogacuna musyapäcö paypa wilacuyninta.  
\v 23 Israel runacuna y mana Israel runacunapis Santu Espíritu munashgannog lapan shongunwan Tayta Diosta adorapäcunanpag cag höra chämushganami. Tsaynog adoranantsitami Tayta Dios munan.  
\v 24 Tayta Diosnintsega Espiritumi caycan. Tsaymi lapan shonguntsiwan maychöpis payta adorashun.” 
\p  
\v 25 Tsauraga tsay warmi nergan: “Cristo shamunanpag cashganta musyämi, tayta. Pay shamurnami tsaycunata tantyatsimäshunpag.” 
\p  
\v 26 Tsaymi Jesús caynog nergan: “Tsay shamunanpag cäga nogami caycä.” 
\p  
\v 27 Micuyta rantimushganpita cutiycurmi discïpuluncuna Jesusta tarergan tsay warmiwan parlaycagta. Tsaymi quiquinpura caynog nir parlapäcorgan: “¿Imanirtag tagay warmiwan Jesús parlaycan?” Itsanga mayganpis manami taporgantsu imapita parlaycashgantapis. 
\p  
\v 28 Tsauraga puynunta cachariycushpan marcaman tsay warmi aywargan runacunata caynog nir wilananpag:  
\v 29 “Juc runami pözu cagcho caycan. Paymi nimashga imanog cashgätapis. Acu aywashun ricapäcunayquipag. ¿Manatsurag pay caycan salvamagnintsi Cristo?” 
\p  
\v 30 Tsauraga runacuna aywapäcorgan Jesús caycashgan cagman payta ricapäcunanpag.  
\v 31 Tsayyäga discïpuluncuna Jesusta nergan: “Micushunna, tayta.” 
\p  
\v 32 Tsauraga Jesús caynog nergan: “Nogapa micuynë jucmi caycan.” 
\p  
\v 33 Tsaymi discïpuluncuna quiquinpura parlar caynog nergan: “¿Pirag micuyta apapämushga micunanpag?” 
\p  
\v 34 Tsaynog yarpashganta tantyarmi Jesús nergan: “Nogapa micuynëga caycan cachamagnë nimashganta ruraymi.  
\v 35 ¡Tantyacäriy! ¡Diospa wilacuyninta chasquicunanpag runacuna listunami carcaycan! Cananpita chuscu quillacho cosëcha listu cananpag cashgannogmi tagay aywaycämog Samaria runacunapis listuna caycan wilacuynëta chasquicunanpag.  
\v 36 Wilacuynëta chasquicorga gloriacho cushishgami imayyagpis cawapäcongapag. Ali cosëcha cashganpita murog cagpis cosechag cagpis cushicushgannogmi Diospa wilacuyninta punta wilacogcuna y guepa wilacogcunapis cushicärin wilacushganta chasquicuptin.” 
\p  
\v 37-38 Nircurnami Jesús nergan: “Diospa wilacuyninta wilacur unay profëtacuna murucognogpis maynami wilacärishga noga shamunäpag cashganta. Tsay unay profëtacuna wilacärishganmanmi gamcunatapis cachaycä wilacuynëta wilacärinayquipag. Tsaymi wilacärishgayquita runacuna wiyar chasquicuptin: ‘Juc muruptinpis jucnami cosechan’ nishgannogla caycan.” 
\p  
\v 39 Marcaman cutiycur: “Jesusmi nimashga imanog cashgätapis” nir tsay warmi wilacuptinmi atsca runacuna criyipäcorgan Tayta Dios cachamushgan Cristo cashganta.  
\v 40 Tsauraga runacuna Jesús cagman chayaycur ruwacärergan paycunawan quëdananpag. Tsaynog ruwacuptinmi paycuna cagcho Jesús goyargan ishcay junag.  
\v 41 Paycuna cagcho goyar wilapaptinmi más atsca runacuna criyipäcorgan Tayta Dios cachamushgan Cristo cashganta.  
\v 42 Tsaymi tsay warmita runacuna caynog nipäcorgan: “¡Gam nipäcamashgayquega rasun cagmi caycan! Cananga quiquëcunanami pay yachatsishganta mayashcä. Tsaymi musyapäcö runacunata salvananpag Tayta Dios cachamushganta.” 
\s1 Autoridäpa tsurinta Jesucristo aliyätsishgan 
\r (Mateo 8.5-13; Lucas 7.1-10) 
\p  
\v 43 Tsaycho ishcay junag goyarcurmi Galilea provinciaman Jesús cutergan.  
\v 44-45 Galileaman cutiptinmi marca mayincuna cushicärergan Jerusalencho milagruta rurashgannog paycuna cagchöpis milagruta rurananpag cashganta yarpar. Jerusalencho milagruta rurashganta ricashga carpis manami criyipäcorgantsu Tayta Diospa wilacognin cashganta. Marca mayincuna tsaynog mana criyiptinmi Jesús caynog nergan: “Tayta Diosnintsipa profëtantaga marca mayincuna manami chasquicärintsu.” 
\p  
\v 46-47 Tsaypitana Jesús cutergan Galilea provinciacho caycag Caná marcaman. Tsaychömi yacuta vïnuman naupata ticratsergan. Canácho cashganta musyaycurmi Capernaum marcapita juc autoridä tsayman aywargan. Chayaycurmi Jesusta ruwacorgan wayinman aywaycur antsa caycag tsurinta aliyätsinanpag.  
\v 48 Tsauraga Jesús caynog nergan: “¿Imanirtag gamcuna milagrutarag ricayta munarcaycanqui Tayta Dios cachamashganta criyipäcunayquipag?” 
\p  
\v 49 Tsaynog niptinpis tsay runa caynog nergan: “Imanog captinpis tsurëta aliyätsinayquipag wayëman jucla aywayculäshun, tayta. Mana aywaptiquega tsurë wanongachari.” 
\p  
\v 50 Tsaynog niptin Jesús nergan: “Tsuriqui aliyashganami caycan. Cananga cushishgana wayiquipa cuticuy.” 
\p Tsauraga Jesús nishganta criyir wayinpa cuticorgan.  
\v 51 Wayinman chayaycaptinnashi ashmaynincuna taripaycur caynog nergan: “¡Tsuriqui aliyashganami caycan, tayta!” 
\p  
\v 52 Tsaynog niptin ashmaynincunata taporgan imay höra aliyashgantapis. Tsauraga ashmaynincuna wilargan ganyan pulan junagna tsurin aliyashganta. 
\p  
\v 53 Tsauraga tsay runa yarpargan Jesús tsay höra: “Tsuriqui aliyashganami caycan” nishganta. Tsaypitanami tsay runa wayincho cagcunawan criyipäcorgan Jesusga Tayta Dios cachamushgan Cristo cashganta. 
\p  
\v 54 Tsay wamrata aliyätsishganwanga ishcay cutinami milagruta Jesús rurargan Galilea provinciacho. 
\c 5  
\s1 Betesda pözucho puriyta mana puëdeg runata Jesucristo aliyätsishgan 
\p  
\v 1 Tsaypitana Jerusalencho Tayta Diosta adorapäcunanpag fiesta captin Jesuspis aywargan tsay fiestaman.  
\v 2 Jerusalén yaycunachömi “Uysha yargunan” nishgan puncu caycan. Tsaychömi caycan jatun pözu. Hebreo idiömachöga tsay pözupa jutin caycan Betesdami. Tsay jatun pözupa naupanchöga caycan pitsga alarcunami.  
\v 3 Pitsgan alarcunachömi jitarpaycargan atsca gueshyaycag runacuna, gapra runacuna y puriyta mana puëdeg runacunapis.  
\v 4 [Tsaychömi paycuna shuyarpaycargan ciëlupita ángil urarcamur yacuta cuyutsipänanpag. Yacuta cuyurcatsiptinna maygan gueshyagpis puntata yacuman yaycog cäga aliyashgana yargamog.] 
\p  
\v 5 Tsaychömi juc runa gueshyar jitaraycargan quimsa chunca pusag (38) watana.  
\v 6 Tsay runa unaypitana gueshyashganta musyarmi Jesús caynog taporgan: “¿Aliyashga cayta munanquicu?” 
\p  
\v 7 Tsaynog niptinmi tsay gueshyaycag runa nergan: “Au, aliyashga caytami munä, tayta. Tsaynog captinpis manami pïnëpis cantsu yacuta ángil cuyutsiptin jatun pözuman yaycatsimänanpag. Yaycunäpag caycaptëpis jucmi yaliman.” 
\p  
\v 8 Tsaynog niptinmi Jesús caynog nergan: “¡Sharcuy! Quirmayquita apacurcur aywacuy.” 
\p  
\v 9-10 Tsaynog niptin tsay gueshyaycag runa jinan höra aliyargan. Nircurna quirmanta apacurcur cushishga aywacorgan. 
\p Quirmanta apaycagta ricarmi Israel runacunapa autoridänincuna caynog nergan: “Sábado jamay junag caycaptenga ¿imanirtag quirmayqui apashga aywaycanqui?” 
\p  
\v 11 Tsauraga tsay runa caynog nergan: “Aliyätsimagnë runami nimashga quirmäta apacurcur aywacunäpag.” 
\p  
\v 12 Tsaymi tsay runata tapupäcorgan caynog nir: “¿Pitag tsaynog nishushcanqui?” 
\p  
\v 13 Tsaynog tapuptin pï aliyätsishgantapis manami musyargantsu, atsca runacuna tsaycho captin. 
\p  
\v 14 Tsaypitana tsay aliyätsishgan runawan templucho tincurcur Jesús nergan: “Aliyashgana caycarga amana yapay jutsata ruraynatsu. Jutsata yapay rurarga gueshyashgayquipitapis masmi imapis pasashunquipag.” 
\p  
\v 15 Tsaynog niptin tsay runa autoridäcunaman aywar wilargan aliyätsegnin runa Jesús cashganta.  
\v 16 Wilaptinmi autoridäcuna Jesuspa contran sharcapäcorgan sábado jamay junagcho aliyätsishganpita. 
\p  
\v 17 Tsaypitanami paycunawan tincur Jesús caynog nergan: “Taytä alita rurashgannogmi nogapis alita rurar tsay runata aliyätsishcä, sábado jamay junag captinpis.” 
\p  
\v 18 Tsaynog niptinmi autoridäcuna Jesusta wanutsiyta munapäcorgan. Tsaynog wanutsiyta munargan manami sábado jamay junagcho runata aliyätsishgalanpitatsu, sinöga: “Diosmi Taytä” nishganpitami. “Diosmi Taytä” niptin paycuna yarpapäcorgan Dios-tucuycashganta. 
\s1 Diospa tsurin car Jesucristo munayniyog cashgan 
\p  
\v 19 Tsauraga Jesús caynog nergan: “Diospa tsurin carmi lapantapis rurä Taytä munashgannogla.  
\v 20 Imatapis ruranäpäga Taytäragmi cuyay tsurin captë tantyatsiman. Tsaymi runacunata aliyätsishgalätatsu ricanquipag, sinöga más espantaypag cag milagrutapis ricanquipagmi.  
\v 21 Tsaymi juicio final junag wanushcunata Taytä cawaritsimunanpag munayniyog cashgannog nogapis munayniyog caycä runacunata perdonar mushog cawayta gonäpag. 
\p  
\v 22 “Tsaynogpis juicio final junag Taytä manami pitapis juzgangatsu, sinöga tsurin captë nogatami nimashga pï-maytapis juzganäpag.  
\v 23 Tsaynog nimashga quiquinta respitashgannogla nogatapis lapan runacuna respitamänanpagmi. Tsaymi nogata mana respitamag cäga Taytätapis mana respitaycantsu. 
\p  
\v 24 “Shumag tantyacäriy. Wilacuynëta chasquicur cachamagnë Taytäman yäracogcunaga infiernuman manami gaycushgatsu canga, sinöga gloriachömi imayyagpis cawangapag.  
\v 25 Tsaynogpis wilacuynëta chasquicorga wanushganog cashganpita mushog cawaytami chasquengapag. Tsay cawayta gonäpag cag höra maynami chämushgana. Tsaynoglami höra chämonga wanushcunatapis cawaritsimunäpag.  
\v 26 Pitapis cawayta gonanpag Tayta Dios munayniyog cashgannogmi nogapis munayniyog caycä pitapis mushog cawayta gonäpag.  
\v 27 Tsaynoglami Tayta Diospita \nd noga\nd* shamushga captë lapan runacunata juzganäpag churamashga. 
\p  
\v 28 “Ama yarpapäcuytsu wanushcunata mana cawaritsimunäpag cashganta. Höran chämuptenga lapan wanushcunatami cawaritsimushag.  
\v 29 Alita ruragcunaga cawarircamur imayyagpis gloriachömi cawapäcongapag. Mana alita ruragcunami itsanga cawarimurpis infiernucho imayyagpis nacapäcongapag.  
\v 30 Cachamagnë Taytä munashgantami imaypis rurä. Tsaymi pay munashgannogla lapan runacunata juzgashagpag. 
\s1 Tayta Dios cachamushganta Jesucristo tantyatsishgan 
\p  
\v 31-32 “Tayta Dios cachamashgantaga manami quiquilätsu në, sinöga milagrucunata ruranäpag yanapamashpan Tayta Diospis runacunata musyaycätsinmi paypita shamushgäta. Tsaynog musyaycätsishuptiquega tantyapäcuy nishgäcuna rasunpa cashganta. 
\p  
\v 33 “Tsaynoglami Tayta Dios cachamashganta Juan Bautistapis wilacushga.  
\v 34-35 Tsaynog wilacuptin atscagmi cushicärergan shamunäpag cagta musyashpan. Nogapita Juan wilacushganta yarpaycätsë manami ali wilacog cashganta yarpänayquipagtsu, sinöga Tayta Dios cachamashganta criyishpayqui salvacärinayquipagmi. 
\p  
\v 36 “Nogapita Juan wilacushganta mana criyirpis milagro rurashgäcunata ricar y yachatsishgäcunata mayarga Tayta Dios cachamashganta criyipäcuy.  
\v 37 Tsaynogpami quiquin mana parlapäshushpayquipis y mana yuripäshushpayquipis Tayta Dios musyaycätsishunqui nogata cachamashganta.  
\v 38 Tsaynog musyaycätsishuptiquipis nogata mana chasquicamarga Tayta Diostapis manami chasquicurcaycanquitsu. 
\s1 Runacuna mana chasquicushganpita Jesucristo parlashgan 
\p  
\v 39 “Gamcunaga Tayta Diosnintsipa palabranta liyir yachacurcaycanqui gloriaman chayayta munarmi. Tsaynog yachacurpis manami tantyapäcunquitsu tsay escribishgancuna noga shamunäpag escribiraycashganta.  
\v 40 Tsaymi nogata chasquicamayta mana munarga Tayta Diosnintsipa palabranta mayjina yachacurpis gloriaman imaypis mana chayanquipagtsu. 
\p  
\v 41-42 “Noga musyämi janan shongula Tayta Diosman yäracuycashgayquita. Tsaymi gamcuna mana chasquicamaptiquipis nogaga imaypis Taytä nimashganta ruraycäshag. 
\p  
\v 43 “Tayta Diospita shamushga captëpis gamcunaga chasquicamayta manami munapäcunquitsu. Quiquilanpa yarpaynilanpita shamog runacuna nishgancunatami itsanga chasquicurcaycanqui.  
\v 44 Tsaynog chasquicurcaycanqui paycunapita ali ricashga cayta munarmi. Tsaynog caycarga ¿imanirtag yarparcaycanqui Tayta Dios munashgannog cawaycashgayquita? 
\p  
\v 45-46 “Gamcuna yarpapäcunqui nogata mana chasquicamarpis Moisés escribishgan leycunata cumplir salvacärinayquipag cashganta. Tsaynog yarpaptiquipis Moisesga noga shamunäpag cagpitami escribergan. Moisés escribishgancunata rasunpa chasquicushpayquega noga nishgäcunatapis chasquicärinquimanmi. Mana chasquicushgayquipitami juicio final junag Taytäpa naupancho Moisespis nishunquipag jutsayog cashgayquita.  
\v 47 Nogapita Moisés escribishgantapis mana chasquicuycarga ¿imanogparag noga nishgäcunata chasquicärinquiman?” 
\c 6  
\s1 Pitsga waranga runacuna micapäcunanpag milagruta Jesucristo rurashgan 
\r (Mateo 14.13-21; Marcos 6.30-44; Lucas 9.10-17) 
\p  
\v 1 Tsaypitanami Galilea lagünata Jesús tsimpargan. (Cananga tsay lagünata nipäcun “Tiberias.”)  
\v 2 Gueshyagcunata aliyätsishganta ricarmi paypa guepanta atsca runacuna aywapäcorgan.  
\v 3 Tsaychönami lömaman aywaycur discïpuluncunawan Jesús jamacärergan.  
\v 4 (Tsay witsan Pascua aniversario chaycämorgannami.)  
\v 5 Paycuna caycashganman atsca runacuna chaycämushganta ricarmi Felipita Jesús caynog nergan: “Caytsica runacunapäga ¿maypitatag micuyta rantimushun?” 
\p  
\v 6 Tsaynog nergan: “Mä imanimänagshi Felipe” nishpanmi. Jesús musyargannami imanogpa micuyta camaripänanpag cashgantapis.  
\v 7 Tsauraga Felipe caynog nergan: “Pusag (8) quilla gänapacushgantsiwannog rantimuptintsipis manami aypanmantsu caytsica runacuna walca walcala micapäcunanpagpis.” 
\p  
\v 8 Tsaymi Simón Pedrupa wauguin Andrés nergan:  
\v 9 “Caycho juc wamra tsararaycan pitsga cebäda tantata y ishcay pescädulatami, tayta.” 
\p  
\v 10 Niptinmi Jesús discïpuluncunata nergan: “Lapan runacunata nipäcuy jamacunanpag.” 
\p Tsaymi jamacunanpag discïpuluncuna niptin pashpaman lapan runacuna jamacärergan. Tsaychömi olgu cagcunalata yupaptin cargan pitsga waranganog (5,000).  
\v 11 Nircurnami tsay pitsga tantata y ishcay pescäducunata Jesús aptarcur Tayta Diosta manacur agradëcicorgan. Agradëcicurcurnami discïpuluncunata macyargan runacunata aypunanpag. 
\p  
\v 12 Lapan runacuna sacsashganyag micurcuptinnami discïpuluncunata Jesús nergan: “Putsushgancunata lapanta shuntamuy.” 
\p  
\v 13 Tsaynog niptinmi putsushgan tantata discïpuluncuna shuntargan chunca ishcay (12) canasta juntata. 
\p  
\v 14 Tsay milagro rurashganta ricaycurmi runacuna cushicushpan caynog nipäcorgan: “Cay runaga Tayta Dios cachamunanpag cag profëta imachari caycan.”\f + \fr 6:14 \ft Tsay profëtapita masta musyanayquipag liyinqui Deuteronomio 18.15,18.\f* 
\p  
\v 15 Tsaynog nishpanmi runacuna imanogpapis nacionninpa mandagnin rey cananpag churayta munapäcorgan. Tsaynog churananta mana munarmi jircapa Jesús japalan aywacorgan. 
\s1 Yacu jananpa Jesucristo purishgan 
\r (Mateo 14.22-27; Marcos 6.45-52) 
\p  
\v 16 Patsa tsacaycaptinnami Jesuspa discïpuluncuna cutergan lagüna cuchunman.  
\v 17 Jesusmi itsanga jircapita manarag cutimorganragtsu. Tsaymi büquiman witsarcur discïpuluncunala Capernaum marcaman aywaycargan.  
\v 18 Aywaycaptinmi fiyupa wayraptin yacu pulchagyayta galaycorgan.  
\v 19 Tsaypita juc lëwatanog aywaycarna Jesusta ricapäcorgan yacu jananpa paycuna cagman aywaycagta. Payta ricaycurmi fiyupa mantsacorgan.  
\v 20 Tsauraga Jesús caynog nergan: “¡Ama mantsacamaytsu! ¡Nogami caycä!” 
\p  
\v 21 Tsaynog niptinmi büquita ichitsipäcorgan Jesús witsänanpag. Tsaypita maylantanami lagüna cuchunman chayapäcorgan. 
\s1 Jesucristo imayyagpis cawatsicog micuyman tincutsicushgan 
\p  
\v 22 Milagruta Jesús rurashgan cagcho quëdag runacuna ricargan tsaycho caycag juclayla büquiwan discïpuluncuna aywacärishgantami. Paycunawan Jesús mana aywashga captinmi yarpapäcorgan jircacho quëdacushganta.  
\v 23-24 Tsauraga Jesustapis ni discïpuluncunatapis mana tarishpanmi Tiberias marcapita büquicuna chayaptin tsay büquicunawanna Capernaum marcaman tsay runacuna aywapäcorgan Jesusta ashinanpag. 
\p  
\v 25 Capernaumcho Jesusta tariycurmi payta tapupäcorgan: “Tayta, ¿imay höratag cayman shamorgayqui?” 
\p  
\v 26 Tsauraga Jesús nergan: “Gamcuna ashircaycämanqui manami Tayta Dios cachamashganta tantyartsu, sinöga sacsagpag micushgalayquipitami.  
\v 27 Pachalayquipäga ama yarpachacuytsu. Tsaypa trucanga yarpachacäriy mana ushacag cawayta taripäcunayquipag. Tsay cawaytaga \nd nogapitaragmi\nd* chasquinquipag. Tsaypagmi Tayta Diosnintsi churamashga.” 
\p  
\v 28 Tsaynog niptinmi paycuna tapupäcorgan: “Tayta, ¿imatatag rurapäcöman gloriaman aywapäcunäpag?” 
\p  
\v 29 Tsauraga Jesús caynog nergan: “Gloriaman aywanayquipäga nishgäcunata chasquicäriy. Tsaytami Tayta Dios munan. Yäracamagcunata gloriaman pushanäpagmi Tayta Dios cachamashga.” 
\p  
\v 30 Tsaynog niptinmi caynog nipäcorgan: “Nishgayquicunata chasquicunäpäga mä ricanäpag milagruta ruray.  
\v 31 Chunyag tsaqui jircacho unay Israel mayintsicunapag maná nishgan micuyta Moisés camaripashgannog gampis mä nogacunapag micuyta waran waran camaripämay. Micuyta Moisés camaripashganpitaga Tayta Diosnintsipa palabranchöpis caynogmi niycan: 
\q1 ‘Tayta Diosmi jana patsapita micuyta paycunapag camaripargan.’\x + \xo 6:31 \xt Éxodo 16.4; Salmo 78.24\x* 
\m Tsaynogla gampis nogacunapag camarimuy.” 
\p  
\v 32 Tsauraga Jesús caynog nergan: “Shumag tantyacäriy. Moisés unay camaripashgan micuyga manami runacuna imayyagpis cawananpagtsu cargan. Cananmi itsanga runacuna imayyagpis cawananpag Taytä gloriapita juc micuytana camarimushga.  
\v 33 Tsay micuytaga maynami ciëlupita cachamushga. Tsay micuyta micurmi runacuna imayyagpis gloriacho cawangapag.” 
\p  
\v 34 Tsauraga paycuna nipäcorgan: “Tsay micuytaga waran waran camaripaycalämay, tayta.” 
\p  
\v 35 Tsaynog niptinmi Jesús nergan: “Imayyagpis cawatsicog micuyga nogami caycä. Nogata chasquicamag cäga sacsagpag micushgannogmi imaypis cushishga cawanga. Tsaynogpis nogaman yäracamag cäga yacuta yamashganyag upushgannogmi imaypis cushishga cawanga.  
\v 36 Tsaynog captinpis gamcunaga yachatsishgäcunata mayaycarpis y milagro rurashgäcunata ricaycarpis manami chasquicamanquitsu. 
\p  
\v 37 “Gamcuna mana chasquicamaptiquipis Taytä acrashgan cagcunaga lapanpis nogata chasquicamanmi. Nogata chasquicamagtaga manami pitapis gargushagtsu.  
\v 38-39 Gargunäpa trucanga nogata chasquicamag cagtaga lapantapis juicio final junag cawaritsimushag. Taytä manami munantsu nogaman yäracamagcuna mayganpis guepaman cuticunanta. Paycunata shumag ricanäpagmi cay patsaman Taytä cachamashga.  
\v 40 Tsaynogpami chasquicamagcunataga cawaritsimushag gloriacho imayyagpis cawananpag. Tsaycho cawanantami Taytä munan.” 
\p  
\v 41 Gloriapita shamog micuy cashganta Jesús niptinmi tsaycho caycag Israel runacunapa autoridänincuna caynog nipäcorgan:  
\v 42 “Cay runaga ¿manacu Josëpa tsurin? Nogantsega musyantsimi maman y taytan pï cashgantapis. ¿Imanirtag payga: ‘Gloriapitami shamushcä’ niycämantsi?” 
\p  
\v 43 Tsaynog nipäcuptinmi Jesús caynog nergan: “Gamcuna mana tantyashpayquimi tsaynog nircaycanqui.  
\v 44 Cachamagnë Tayta Dios tantyatsishganta chasquicogcunalami nogata chasquicaman. Chasquicamag cagtaga gloriacho imayyagpis cawananpagmi wanuptinpis cawaritsimushag. 
\p  
\v 45 “Tayta Diosnintsipa profëtancuna escribishganchöpis caynogmi niycan: 
\q1 ‘Lapan runacunatapis quiquëmi musyatsishag noga munashgänog cawananpag.’\x + \xo 6:45 \xt Isaías 54.13\x* 
\m Tsay escribirashgannoglami gamcunatapis Tayta Dios musyaycätsishunqui. Tsaynog captinpis pay tantyatsishganta chasquicog cagcunalami nogata chasquicaman.  
\v 46 Gloriapita shamushga car nogalami Tayta Diosta reguë. Manami pipis más paytaga reguintsu.  
\v 47 Tsaynog captenga nogata chasquicamag caglami Tayta Diospa naupancho imayyagpis cawangapag. 
\p  
\v 48 “Nogaga imayyagpis cawatsicog micuymi caycä.  
\v 49 ¿Manacu chunyag tsaqui jircacho unay Israel mayintsicuna micapäcorgan maná nishgan micuyta? Tsayta micurpis wanupäcorganmi.  
\v 50 Gloriapita shamog micuyta micog cagmi itsanga imayyagpis cawangapag.  
\v 51 Nogami gloriapita shamog cag micuyga caycä. Runacuna gloriacho imayyagpis cawananpagmi noga wanushagpag. Tsaymi nogata micamag cäga wanurpis cawarimonga imayyagpis gloriacho cawananpag.” 
\p  
\v 52 Tsaynog niptinmi tsay autoridäcuna jucninpis jucninpis caynog nipäcorgan: “¿Imanogpatag paytaga micushun?” 
\p  
\v 53 Tsauraga Jesús caynog nergan: “\nd Nogata\nd* mana micamarga y yawarnëta mana uporga manami pipis gloriaman chayangatsu.  
\v 54 Nogata micamag cagtami y yawarnëta upog cagtami itsanga cawaritsimushag gloriacho imayyagpis cawananpag.  
\v 55 Nogaga caycä rasunpa cag micuymi y yawarnëga rasunpa cag yacumi.  
\v 56 Nogata micamag cagwan y yawarnëta upog cagwanmi imaypis caycäshag. 
\p  
\v 57 “Cachamagnë Taytä imayyagpis cawashgannogmi nogapis cawaycä. Tsaynoglami nogata chasquicamag cäga imayyagpis cawanga. Taytäpitarag cawayta chasquishgänoglami nogata chasquicamagcunapis nogapita cawayta chasquircaycan.  
\v 58 Gamcunataga musyaycätsë gloriapita shamog micuy cashgätami. Unay Israel mayintsicuna maná micuyta micurpis wanorganmi. Gloriapita shamog micuyta micog cagmi itsanga gloriacho imayyagpis cushishgala cawangapag.” 
\p  
\v 59 Jesús tsaynog yachatsergan Capernaum sinagogachömi. 
\s1 Jesucristuta imaypis mana cacharinanpag discïpuluncuna nishgan 
\p  
\v 60 Tsay yachatsishganta mayar Jesuspa gatiragnincuna atscagmi caynog nipäcorgan: “Tsaynog parlaptenga ¿pitag paytaga criyenga?” 
\p  
\v 61 Tsaynog niycashganta tantyarmi Jesús caynog nergan: “¿Imanirtag gamcuna tsaynog yarparcaycanqui?  
\v 62 Canan tsaynog yarparpis gloriaman \nd noga\nd* cutiycagta ricamashpayquimi tantyapäcunquipag Tayta Dios cachamashgan Cristo cashgäta.  
\v 63 Noga nishgäcunata chasquicuptiquega Santu Espiritumi yanapashunqui ali cawanayquipag y gloriacho cushishgala imayyagpis cawanayquipag.  
\v 64 Santu Espíritu yanapashunayquipag caycaptinpis waquinniquega nishgäcunata manami chasquicärinquitsu.” 
\p Jesús tsaynog nergan maygan runacunapis payta mana chasquicärishganta musyarmi. Tsaynogpis musyarganmi maygan discïpulun autoridäcunaman payta entregananpag cashgantapis.  
\v 65 Tsauraga Jesús caynog nergan: “Waquinniqui mana chasquicamänayquipag cashganta musyarmi mayna caynog nishcä: ‘Tayta Dios tantyatsishganta chasquicogcunalami nogata chasquicaman.’ ”\x + \xo 6:65 \xt San Juan 6.44\x* 
\p  
\v 66 Tsay nishganta mana tantyarmi atsca runacuna Jesusta cachariycur aywacorgan.  
\v 67 Runacuna tsaynog aywacuptinmi chunca ishcay (12) acrashgan cag discïpuluncunata Jesús nergan: “¿Gamcunapis paycunanog aywacuytacu munarcaycanqui?” 
\p  
\v 68 Tsauraga Simón Pedro nergan: “Gloriaman aywapäcunäpag shumag yachaycätsimaptiquega ¿imata ashirtag maypapis aywapäcöman, tayta?  
\v 69 Nogacunaga criyipäcömi Tayta Dios cachamushgan Cristo cashgayquita.” 
\p  
\v 70 Tsauraga Jesús caynog nergan: “Chunca ishcay (12) acrashgan cag discïpulöcuna canayquipäga nogami gamcunata acrashcä. Tsaynog captinpis gamcunapita jucmi diablo munashganta rurangapag.”  
\v 71 Jesús tsaynog nergan Simonpa tsurin Judas Iscariotipagmi. Chunca ishcay acrashgan cag discïpuluncunapita carpis paymi autoridäcunata pushargan Jesusta prësu tsaripäcunanpag. 
\c 7  
\s1 Ramäda fiestaman Jesucristo aywananta wauguincuna munashgan 
\p  
\v 1 Tsaypitanami Galilea provinciacho cag marcacunapa Jesús purergan. Judea provinciaman manami aywayta munargantsu Israel runacunapa autoridänincuna payta wanutsiyta munapäcuptin.  
\v 2-3 Jerusalencho Ramäda fiestapag walca junagla pishiycaptinmi wauguincuna Jesusta caynog nergan: “Fiestapag Jerusalenman ayway. Tsaychöpis milagrucunata ruray discïpuluyquicuna ricapäcunanpag.  
\v 4 Reguishga cayta munarga manami caylachötsu milagrucunata ruranquiman. Jerusalén marcachöpis milagrucunata ruray lapanpis ricananpag.” 
\p  
\v 5 Jesuspa wauguincuna tsaynog nergan Tayta Dios cachamushgan Cristo cashganta mana criyishpanmi. 
\p  
\v 6 Tsauraga wauguincunata Jesús nergan: “Nogaga manami aywashagragtsu. Gamcunami itsanga imay hörapis aywapäcunquiman.  
\v 7 Tsaychöga runacuna manami chasquicamantsu, jutsata rurashganta niptë. Gamcunatami itsanga chasquicushunqui, jutsata rurashganta mana niptiqui.  
\v 8 Gamcunala aywapäcuy tsay fiestamanga. Manami hörä chämunragtsu tsayman aywanäpäga.” 
\p  
\v 9 Tsaynog nirmi Galilea provinciacho Jesús quëdacorgan. 
\s1 Ramäda fiestaman Jesucristo aywashgan 
\p  
\v 10 Wauguincuna Ramäda fiestaman aywacuptinnami pitapis mana wilapaylapa Jesuspis aywargan.  
\v 11 Fiestacho Jesusta mana ricarmi Israel runacunapa autoridänincuna parlapäcorgan caynog nir: “¿Maychörag tsay runa caycan?” 
\p  
\v 12 Waquin runacuna nipäcorgan Jesús ali runa cashganta. Y waquincunanami nipäcorgan lutanta yachatsir puriycashganta.  
\v 13 Itsanga autoridäcunata mantsacärishpan manami pipis Jesuspita parlacorgantsu runacuna mayayga. 
\p  
\v 14 Ramäda fiesta pulancho caycaptinnami Jerusalenman Jesús chayargan. Nircurnami templo patiuman aywaycur Tayta Diosnintsipa wilacuyninta yachatsergan.  
\v 15 Tsaycho yachatsishganta mayaycur yachag cashganta tantyarmi autoridäcuna nipäcorgan: “Mana estudiashga caycarga ¿imanogpatag cay runa ali yachan?” 
\p  
\v 16 Tsaynog nipäcuptinmi Jesús caynog nergan: “Nogaga yachä cachamagnë Tayta Dios yachatsimashga captinmi. Manami quiquiläpitatsu caynog yachä.  
\v 17 Yachatsishgäcuna Tayta Dios munashgannog cashganta musyayta munarga pay munashgannog cawapäcuy. Tsaynogparagmi tantyapäcunquipag yachatsishgäcuna Tayta Diospita cashganta. 
\p  
\v 18 “Waquin runacunaga, ali ricashga cayta munar, quiquinpa yarpaynilanpitami yachatsir puripäcun. Nogaga manami paycunanogtsu yachatsë, sinöga cachamagnë Tayta Dios munashgannoglami yachatsë.  
\v 19 Gamcunaga Moisés escribishgancunata tsararaycanquimi tsaycunata yachacur Tayta Dios munashgannog cawapäcunayquipag. Tsaynog tsarararpis manami maygayquipis pay munashgannogtsu cawarcaycanqui. Tsaymi wanutsimayta munarcaycanqui.” 
\p  
\v 20 Jesús tsaynog niptinmi runacuna caynog nipäcorgan: “¿Pitag gamta wanutsiyta munaycäshunqui? ¡Demonio imachari gamta löcutaycätsishunqui!” 
\p  
\v 21 Tsaymi Jesús caynog nergan: “Sábado jamay junagcho puriyta mana puëdeg runata aliyätsishgaläpitami\f + \fr 7:21 \ft Puriyta mana puëdeg runata aliyätsishganpita musyanayquipag liyinqui San Juan 5.1-18.\f* gamcunaga wanutsimayta munarcaycanqui.  
\v 22 Tantyacäriy. Moisés yachatsergan olgu wamra yurishganpita pusag (8) junagniyog caycaptin cuerpunta señalatsinantsipagmi. (Moisés yachatsiptinpis tsay costumbrega cargan más unaypitanami.) Moisés escribishgancunata cumplir ¿manacu sábado jamay junag captinpis olgu wamrapa cuerpunta señalapäcunqui?  
\v 23 Olgu wamrayquicunapa cuerpunta sábado jamay junag caycaptinpis señalaycarga ¿imanirtag nogata rabiapaycämanqui sábado jamay junagcho gueshyag runata aliyätsishgäpita?  
\v 24 Pï cashgätapis manarag shumag tantyarga ¿imanirtag jutsayog cashgäta yarpapäcunqui? Shumag juiciuyquiwan parlapäcuy.” 
\s1 Maypita cashgantapis Jesucristo parlashgan 
\p  
\v 25 Tsauraga Jerusalencho tag waquin runacuna quiquinpura parlar caynog nipäcorgan: “¿Manacu cay runataga ashircaycan wanutsinanpag?  
\v 26 Atsca runacunapa naupancho yachatsiptinpis ¿imanirtag autoridäcuna upälacärin? ¿Autoridäcunapis Tayta Dios cachamushgan Cristo cashgantatsurag yarparcaycan?  
\v 27 Manami payga Tayta Dios cachamushgan Cristutsu canman. Musyantsimi may marcapita pay cashgantapis. Tayta Dios cachamushgan Cristo shamuptenga manami pipis musyangapagtsu maypita cashgantapis.” 
\p  
\v 28 Runacuna tsaynog parlaycashgantami templo patiucho yachatsishgan höra Jesús mayargan. Tsaymi caynog nergan: “Gamcuna manami rasunpatsu musyapäcunqui maypita shamushgätapis. Manami quiquëpa munayniläpitatsu cay patsaman shamushcä, sinöga Tayta Dios cachamaptinmi shamushcä.  
\v 29 Tayta Diospita shamushga carmi noga musyä pay imanog cashgantapis.” 
\p  
\v 30 Tsaynog niptinmi waquin runacuna rabiacushpan Jesusta prësu tsaritsiyta munapäcorgan. Itsanga prësu mana tsaripäcorgantsu tsarinanpag cag höra manarag chayaptinmi.  
\v 31 Tsaynog captinpis atscagmi criyipäcorgan Tayta Dios cachamushgan Cristo cashganta. Tsaymi paycuna nipäcorgan: “Milagrucunata rurashganta ricarmi criyintsi Tayta Dios cachamushgan Cristo cashganta.” 
\s1 Fariseo runacuna Jesucristuta prësu tsaritsiyta munashgan 
\p  
\v 32 Runacuna Jesuspa favornin tsaynog niycashganta mayaycurmi fariseo runacunawan mandag cüracuna cachapäcorgan templo täpag wardiacunata Jesusta prësu tsarimunanpag.  
\v 33 Prësu tsaregcuna chayananpäga Jesús caynogmi yachaycätsergan: “Gamcunawanga manami atsca watatsu caycäshagpag. Nogaga cachamagnë Taytä cagmanmi cuticushagpag.  
\v 34 Ashimashpayquipis manami taripäcamanquipagtsu. Noga aywashgä cagmanga manami aywayta camäpacunquipagtsu.” 
\p  
\v 35 Jesús tsaynog niptinmi Israel runacunapa autoridänincuna quiquinpura parlar caynog nipäcorgan: “Mana tarinantsipäga ¿mayparag aywaconga? ¿Juc lädu nacioncho tag marca mayintsicunamantsurag aywanga Diosta mana criyegcunata yachatsinanpag?  
\v 36 ¿Imanirtag ashirpis mana tarinantsipag cashganta niycämantsi? ¿Imanirtag pay aywashgan cagman chayayta mana camäpacunantsipag cashganta niycämantsi?” 
\s1 Jesucristuman yäracogcunapa shonguncho Santu Espíritu cananpag yachatsishgan 
\p  
\v 37 Ramäda fiesta día junagmi\f + \fr 7:37 \ft Israel runacunapa Ramäda fiestanga cargan pusag (8) junagmi. Fiesta ushanan junagragmi día junag cargan. Tsaypita masta musyanayquipag liyinqui Levítico 23.36.\f* lapan runa mayananpag Jesús caynog nergan: “Pasaypa yacunaypanograg Tayta Diospa maquincho cawayta munag cäga nogata chasquicamätsun.  
\v 38 Tayta Diosnintsipa palabrancho nishgannogpis pucyupita chuya yacuta upur cushicushgannogmi chasquicamagcunapis pasaypa cushicongapag.” 
\p  
\v 39 Tsaynog nishpanmi Jesús tantyatsergan runacunapa shonguncho Santu Espíritu cananpag cashganta. Tsay witsanga Santu Espíritu manami chämorganragtsu. Gloriaman Jesús cuticuptinragmi payta chasquicogcunaman Santu Espíritu shamorgan. 
\s1 Jesucristo parlashganpita runacuna rimanacushgan 
\p  
\v 40 Jesús tsaynog nishganta mayaycurmi tsaycho cag waquin runacuna nipäcorgan: “Moisés nishgannog shamunanpag cag profëta\f + \fr 7:40 \ft Tsay profëtapita masta musyanayquipag liyinqui Deuteronomio 18.15,18.\f* imachari payga caycan.” 
\p  
\v 41 Waquin runacuna nipäcorgan: “Paytami Tayta Dios cachamushga salvamänantsipag.” 
\p Y waquinnami nipäcorgan: “Galilea runa caycarga ¿imanogpatag payga Tayta Dios cachamushgan Cristo canman?  
\v 42 Tayta Diosnintsipa palabranchöga niycan mandag rey David castapita Cristo yurinanpag cashgantami. Tsaynogpis niycan Belenchörag yurinanpag cashgantami. Belencho mana yurishga carga manami payga salvamagnintsi Cristo canmantsu.”\x + \xo 7:42 \xt Miqueas 5.2\x* 
\p  
\v 43 Tsaynog nirmi waquincunaga Jesuspa contran parlargan y waquinnami favornin sharcorgan.  
\v 44 Chasquicuyta mana munarmi waquincuna prësu tsariyta munapäcorgan. Tsaynog munarpis manami mayganpis tsarergantsu. 
\s1 Jesús Cristo cashganta autoridäcuna mana criyishgan 
\p  
\v 45 Tsaypitami templo täpag wardiacuna cuticärergan mandag cüracuna y fariseo runacuna cashgan cagman. Cutiycuptinmi tapupäcorgan caynog nir: “¿Imanirtag Jesusta prësu mana apamushcanquitsu?” 
\p  
\v 46 Tsaynog tapuptinmi wardiacuna caynog nipäcorgan: “¡Pay parlashgantanöga manami imaypis mayapäcushcätsu!” 
\p  
\v 47 Tsaynog niptinmi fariseo runacuna nipäcorgan: “¿Gamcunatapis criyitsishushcanquicu Tayta Dios cachamushgan Cristo cashganta?  
\v 48 Tsay runataga manami maygan autoridäcunapis ni fariseo runacunapis criyipäcuntsu Tayta Dios cachamushgan Cristo cashganta.  
\v 49 Mana yachag runacunalami paytaga criyipäcun. ¡Tsay runacunaga manami musyantsu maycho sengan cashgantapis!” 
\p  
\v 50-51 Tsaynog nipäcuptinmi Nicodemo caynog nergan: “Leynintsicuna nishgannogpis puntata quiquin parlashgantarag mayashun imanog cashgantapis ninantsipäga.” (Nicodemoga cargan fariseo runami. Paymi naupata Jesús cagman aywargan paywan parlananpag.) 
\p  
\v 52 Tsauraga paycuna caynog nipäcorgan: “¿Gampis paypa marca mayincu caycanqui favornin sharcunayquipag? ¡Tayta Diosnintsipa palabranchöpis manami imaypis nimantsitsu Galileapita profëta cananpag cashganta!” 
\p  
\v 53 [Tsaypitanami wayincunapana lapan cuticärergan. 
\c 8  
\s1 Runan jarucog warmita Jesucristo perdonashgan 
\p  
\v 1 Tsaypitanami Jesús aywargan Olivos lömaman.  
\v 2 Tsaypita wara tuta templo patiuman cutiptinmi runacuna pay cashgan cagman juntacargan. Tsaychömi Jesús paycunata yachatsergan. 
\p  
\v 3 Tsaymanmi Moisés escribishgan leycunata yachatsegcuna y fariseo runacuna apapäcorgan jutsa rurag warmita. Tsay warmita taripäcorgan runanta jarucuycagta. Tsaynog tariycurmi tsaycho caycag runacunapa naupanman tsay warmita ichiycatsir Jesusta caynog tapupäcorgan:  
\v 4 “Cay warmita taripäcushcä runanta jarucur juc runawan punuycagtami, tayta.  
\v 5 Moisés escribishganchöga nimantsi caynog warmicunataga sagmaycälar wanutsinantsipagmi. Gamga ¿imaninquitag, tayta?” 
\p  
\v 6 Tsaynog tapupäcorgan Jesusta lutanta rimatsiyta munapäcushpanmi.\f + \fr 8:6 \ft Roma runacuna, Israel runacunapa mandagnin car, manami munargantsu Israel runacuna pitapis wanutsinanta. Tsaymi: “Moisés escribishgancho nishgannog sagmashun” Jesús niptenga: “¿Imanirtag Roma autoridäcuna michämashgantsita ruranantsipag niycämantsi?” nipäcunman cargan. “Ama sagmashuntsu” niptinpis: “¿Imanirtag mana cäsunquitsu Moisés escribishganta?” nipäcunman cargan.\f* Tsaynog tapuptinmi Jesús dëdunwan escribergan pampacho.  
\v 7 Yaparir yaparir tapupäcuptinnami ichircur Jesús caynog nergan: “Maygayquipis jutsaynag carga mä tsay warmita sagmapäcuy.”  
\v 8 Tsaynog nircurmi pampacho yapay escribergan. 
\p  
\v 9 Tsauraga tsaynog nishganta mayaycärishpanmi auquincunapita galaycur lapanpis juc juclayla yargurir yargurir aywacärergan. Lapan aywacäriptinnami tsay warmilana Jesuspa naupancho quëdargan.  
\v 10 Tsauraga tsay warmita Jesús caynog nergan: “¿Maytag sagmashunayquipag pushamushogniquicuna? ¿Manacu ni juclaylapis sagmashushcanqui?” 
\p  
\v 11 Tsaynog niptin tsay warmi nergan: “Manami mayganpis sagmamashgatsu, tayta.” 
\p Tsauraga Jesús nergan: “Nogapis manami munätsu sagmashga canayquita. Cananga wayiquipana aywacuy. Itsanga amana jutsata ruraynatsu.”] 
\s1 Runacunapag atsquinog Jesucristo cashgan 
\p  
\v 12 Tsaypitanami runacunata Jesús caynog nergan: “Cay patsacho runacunapäga atsquinogmi caycä. Tsaymi nogata chasquicamag cäga manami Satanaspa munayninchönatsu canga, sinöga Tayta Diospa maquincho car atsquichönog cushishga cawangapag.” 
\p  
\v 13 Tsaynog niptinmi fariseo runacuna nipäcorgan: “Tsaynog cashgayquita quiquilayqui niycaptiquega ¿imanogpatag nogacuna criyipäcöman?” 
\p  
\v 14 Tsaynog nipäcuptinmi Jesús nergan: “Quiquilä niptëpis noga nishgäcunaga rasun cagmi caycan. Taytäpa naupanpita shamushgäta y tsayman cuticunäpag cashgantapis musyämi. Gamcunaga manami musyapäcunquitsu maypita shamushgäta y mayman cuticunäpag cashgantapis.  
\v 15 Tsaymi yarpaynilayquipita juzgaycämanqui. Nogaga manami gamcunanogtsu pitapis juzgä.  
\v 16 Cachamagnë Taytä nogawan imaypis captinmi pitapis juzgarga rasun caglata juzgä. 
\p  
\v 17 “Moisés escribishganchöpis caynogmi niycan: 
\q1 ‘Ishcay testïgucuna tsay yarpayla niptinragmi criyipäcunquiman imapis rasun cag cashganta.’\x + \xo 8:17 \xt Deuteronomio 19.15\x* 
\m  
\v 18 Tsay nishgannoglami ishcay testïgucuna caycan Tayta Dios cachamashgan Cristo cashgäta ninanpag. Cachamagnë Taytämi juc testïgo, y jucag testïgöga quiquëmi caycä.” 
\p  
\v 19 Tsaynog niptinmi tapupäcorgan: “Nishgayqui rasunpa cashganta tapupäcunäpag ¿maychötag taytayqui caycan?” 
\p Tsauraga Jesús nergan: “Gamcunaga manami musyapäcunquitsu Taytä pï cashgantapis ni noga pï cashgätapis. Noga pï cashgäta musyarga Taytä pï cashgantapis musyanquimanmi.” 
\p  
\v 20 Templucho Jesús tsaynog nergan ofrendata shuntacuna churarashgan cagchömi. Runacunapa naupancho yachatsiptinpis manami pipis payta prësu tsarergantsu, prësu tsarinanpag cag höra manarag chayaptin. 
\s1 Jesucristo pï cashgantapis runacuna mana tantyashgan 
\p  
\v 21 Tsauraga Jesús nergan: “Jutsata rurashgayquipita mana perdonashga carmi gamcunaga aywanäpag cashgan cagman imaypis mana chayanquipagtsu. Tsaymi aywacuptë ashimarpis mana taripäcamanquipagtsu.” 
\p  
\v 22 Tsaynog niptinmi Israel runacunapa autoridänincuna nipäcorgan: “¿Imanirtag aywacunanpag cashganta niycämantsi? ¿Wanutsicuytatsurag payga yarpaycan? Tsaychari pay cashgan cagman mana chayanantsipag cashgantaga niycämantsi.” 
\p  
\v 23 Tsauraga Jesús nergan: “Nogaga gloriapitami shamushcä. Gamcunaga cay patsacho yureglami carcaycanqui.  
\v 24 Tsaymi pï cashgäta wilaptëpis mana criyipäcamanquitsu. Tsaynog mana criyipäcamashgayquipitami gloriaman imaypis mana chayanquipagtsu.” 
\p  
\v 25 Tsaynog niptin caynog nipäcorgan: “Tsaynog parlanayquipäga ¿pitag gam canqui?” 
\p Tsauraga Jesús nergan: “Pï cashgätapis maynami wilashcä.  
\v 26 Gamcunata tantyatsinäpag atscaragmi caycan. Tsaynog captinpis noga yachatsishgäcuna manami quiquëpa yarpayniläpitatsu caycan, sinöga cachamagnë Taytä tantyatsimashgalanmi. Pay nimashgancunaga lapanpis rasun caglami caycan.” 
\p  
\v 27 Jesús tsaynog parlapaycaptinpis paycunaga manami tantyapäcorgantsu Tayta Diosnintsi paypa taytan cashganta.  
\v 28 Tsaynog mana tantyapäcuptinmi Jesús nergan: “\nd Noga\nd* pï cashgäta canan mana tantyarpis wanutsimashgayqui hörami tantyapäcunquipag pï cashgäta y Taytä nimashgannogla wilacushgätapis.  
\v 29 Cachamagnë Taytäga imaypis nogawanmi caycan. Pay munashgannogla ruraptëmi imaypis yanapaycäman.” 
\p  
\v 30 Jesús tsaynog niptinmi atsca criyipäcorgan Tayta Dios cachamushgan Cristo cashganta. 
\s1 Jesucristuta mana chasquicogcuna diablupa munaynincho cashgan 
\p  
\v 31 Tsaypitanami payman criyeg Israel runacunapa autoridänincunata Jesús caynog nergan: “Yachatsishgänogla imaypis cawarga rasunpami discïpulöcuna canquipag.  
\v 32 Tsaynog cawarmi tantyapäcunquipag yachatsishgäcuna rasun cag cashganta. Tsaynog tantyacorga manami diablupa munayninchönatsu cawapäcunquipag.” 
\p  
\v 33 Tsaynog niptinmi caynog nipäcorgan: “Abrahampa castan caycaptëga ¿imanirtag tsaynog nipäcamanqui? Nogacunaga manami imaypis diablupa munayninchötsu cawapäcushcä, sinöga Tayta Diospa maquilanchömi.” 
\p  
\v 34 Tsauraga Jesús nergan: “Shumag tantyacäriy. Jutsa ruraycho cawarga manami Tayta Diospa maquinchötsu cawaycanqui. Jutsata rurag cäga lapanpis diablupa munayninchömi carcaycan.  
\v 35 Diablupa munaynincho cawarga manami Diospa wamrantsu caycan, sinöga diablupami. Nogaga Diospa tsurin carmi munayniyog caycä diablupa munaynincho caycagcunata jorgunäpag.  
\v 36 Diablupa munaynincho cashgayquipita noga jorguptëmi Tayta Diospa wamran rasunpa canquipag. 
\p  
\v 37 “Musyämi Abrahampa castan gamcuna cashgayquita. Abrahampa castan caycarpis manami nishgäcunata chasquicamanquitsu. Chasquicamänayquipa trucanga ¿imanirtag wanutsimayta munarcaycanqui?  
\v 38 Taytäpa naupancho caycar musyashgäcunatami gamcunata wilapaycä. Tsaynog wilapaptëpis gamcunaga taytayqui munashgalantami rurarcaycanqui.” 
\p  
\v 39 Tsauraga paycuna nipäcorgan: “¡Abrahampa castan captë paymi nogacunapa taytäga!” 
\p Tsaynog nipäcuptinmi Jesús caynog nergan: “Abrahampa castan caycarpis manami pay cawashgannogtsu cawarcaycanqui.  
\v 40 Abrahamga manami imaypis yarpargantsu Tayta Diospa wilacogninta wanutsiyta. Gamcunaga wanutsimayta munarcaycanqui Tayta Dios nimashgancunata wilacuptëmi.  
\v 41 Mana chasquicamaptiquimi musyacaycan gamcunapa taytayqui diablo cashganta. Tsaymi pay rurashgannogla imaypis rurarcaycanqui.” 
\p Tsaynog niptin paycuna nipäcorgan: “Nogacunapa Taytäga Tayta Diosmi. Manami diablupa tsurintsu capäcö.” 
\p  
\v 42 Tsauraga Jesús caynog nergan: “Tayta Dios rasunpa taytayqui captenga nogata cuyamanquimanmi. Paymi gloriapita cachamashga cay patsaman shamunäpag. Manami quiquëpa munayniläpitatsu noga shamushcä.  
\v 43 ¿Imanirtag gamcuna mana tantyamanquitsu nishgäcunata? Chasquicamayta mana munarmi yaparir yaparir niptëpis gamcunaga mana tantyacunquitsu. 
\p  
\v 44 “Gamcunapa taytayquega diablumi caycan. Tsaymi pay munashgalanta imatapis rurarcaycanqui. Unaypita-patsa runa wanutseg pay cashgannogmi gamcunapis nogata wanutsimayta munarcaycanqui. Tsaynogpis lula carmi diabloga imaypis rasun cagtaga mana rimantsu.  
\v 45 Nogaga rasun caglatami Tayta Diosnintsipa wilacuyninta gamcunata yachatsë. Tayta Diosnintsipa wilacuyninta chasquicuyta mana munarmi nogatapis mana chasquicamanquitsu. 
\p  
\v 46 “Jutsata imaypis mana rurashga captëmi maygayquipis mana careamanquimantsu noga jutsayog cashgäta. Rasun cagta wilacuycaptëga ¿imanirtag mana chasquicamanquitsu?  
\v 47 Tayta Dios taytayqui captenga wilacuyninta cäsucärinquimanmi. Wilacuyninta mana cäsucäriptiquimi musyä Diospa wamran mana cashgayquita.” 
\s1 Abraham manarag yuriptinpis Jesucristo mayna caycashgan 
\p  
\v 48 Tsaynog niptinmi tsay autoridäcuna caynog nipäcorgan: “¡Gamga Samaria runacunanogmi lutanta rimaycanqui! ¡Gamtaga demoniumi mepareci löcutaycätsishunqui!” 
\p  
\v 49 Tsauraga Jesús nergan: “Nogaga manami löcutsu caycä, sinöga Taytä munashgalantami parlaycä. Tsaynog parlaptëpis gamcunaga mana tantyashpayquimi chiquiycämanqui.  
\v 50 Runacuna chasquicamaptinpis o mana chasquicamaptinpis nogaga Taytä munashgannoglami wilacuycä. Mana chasquicamag cagtaga Taytämi juzganga.  
\v 51 Nishgäcunata chasquicogcunami itsanga gloriaman chayar imaypis mana wanongapagtsu.” 
\p  
\v 52 Tsauraga autoridäcuna caynog nipäcorgan: “Cananmi itsanga rasunpa musyapäcö demonio löcutaycätsishushgayquita. Abraham y Tayta Diosnintsipa profëtancunapis lapanmi wanupäcushga. Tsaynog caycaptinpis gamga niycanqui: ‘Nishgäcunata chasquicogcunaga manami wanongapagtsu.’  
\v 53 Tsaynog nerga ¿mana wanunayquipag cashgantacu yarpaycanqui? Mana wanunayquipäga manami Abrahampita más munayniyogtsu caycanqui. Paypis y Tayta Diosnintsipa profëtancunapis wanushga caycaptenga ¿pï cashgayquitatag gamga yarpanqui?” 
\p  
\v 54 Tsauraga Jesús caynog nergan: “Tsaynog nishgäpitaga ama yarpapäcuytsu alabacuycashgäta. Taytä cachamashga captinmi rasun caglata niycä. Gamcunaga Taytäta ‘Diosnëmi’ niycarga ¿imanirtag mana criyimanquitsu nishgäcunata?  
\v 55 Taytä imanog cashgantapis gamcuna manami musyapäcunquitsu. Nogami itsanga lapanta musyä imanog cashgantapis. Tsaymi Taytä nimashgancunalata parlaycä. Gamcuna munashgayquinog yachatserga manami rasun cagtatsu parläman, sinöga gamcunanoglami lulacuycäman.  
\v 56 ‘Abrahampa castanmi nogacuna caycä’ niptiquipis Abrahamga manami gamcunanogtsu cargan. Payga cushicorganmi cay patsaman shamunäpag cashganta musyashpan.” 
\p  
\v 57 Tsauraga autoridäcuna Jesusta nipäcorgan: “Manaragpis pitsga chunca (50) watayog caycarga ¿imanogpatag Abrahamta reguinquiman cargan?” 
\p  
\v 58 Tsaynog niptinmi Jesús caynog nergan: “Tantyacäriy. Abraham manaragpis yuriptin nogaga maynami caycargäna.” 
\p  
\v 59 Jesús tsaynog niptinmi rumita aptacärergan sagmaypa wanutsipäcunanpag. Tsauraga sagmayta munapäcuptinmi runacunapa chaupinpa pasarir templo patiupita Jesús aywacorgan. 
\c 9  
\s1 Gapra runata Jesucristo aliyätsishgan 
\p  
\v 1 Jerusalencho puriycarmi Jesuspa discïpuluncuna ricargan yurishganpita-patsa gapra runata.  
\v 2 Tsaymi Jesusta tapupäcorgan caynog nir: “Tayta, ¿imanirtag cay runa gapra yurishga? ¿Mamanpa y taytanpa jutsanpitacu o quiquinpa jutsanpitacu?” 
\p  
\v 3 Tsaynog tapuptinmi Jesús caynog nergan: “Manami quiquinpa ni mamanpa ni taytanpa jutsanpitatsu gapra yurishga, sinöga aliyätsiptë Tayta Dios munayniyog cashganta runacuna tantyacunanpagmi.  
\v 4 Tsaymi cay patsacho cashgäyag cachamagnë Tayta Dios munashgannog runacunata aliyaycätsë.  
\v 5 Cay patsacho cashgäyäga runacunapag atsquinogmi caycä.” 
\p  
\v 6 Tsaynog nishpanmi pampaman Jesús togaycur mituta rurargan. Nircurna tsay mituwan gaprapa nawinta lushipargan.  
\v 7 Lushiparcurmi caynog nergan: “Siloé nishgan pözuman ayway tsaycho maylacamunayquipag.” 
\p (Siloé ninanga “Cachamushga” ninanmi.) 
\p Tsauraga Jesús nishgannog maylacaramurnami ricaycarna cutergan.  
\v 8 Tsaymi vecïnuncuna y payta reguegcuna caynog nipäcorgan: “¿Manacu cay runaga limushnata manacog gapra runa caycan?” 
\p  
\v 9 Waquincuna nipäcorgan: “Au, paymi.” 
\p Waquincunanami nipäcorgan: “Manami paytsu. Itsanga pay-niragmi.” 
\p Tsaynog niptinmi quiquin caynog nergan: “Au, nogami yurishgäpita-patsa gapra cargä.” 
\p  
\v 10 Tsauraga payta tapupäcorgan: “¿Imanogpatag nawiqui aliyashga?” 
\p  
\v 11 Tsaynog tapuptinmi caynog nergan: “Jesusmi togayninwan mituta rurarcur nawëta lushipämashga. Nircurnami cachamashga Siloé nishgan pözuman nawëta maylacunäpag. Tsaycho maylacushgäpitami cananga nawë ricaycanna.” 
\p  
\v 12 Tsauraga payta yapay tapupäcorgan: “¿Maychötag caycan tsay aliyätsishogniqui runaga?” 
\p Tsaynog tapuptin nergan: “Manami musyätsu maycho caycashgantapis.” 
\s1 Aliyashga runata fariseo runacuna tapupäcushgan 
\p  
\v 13 Tsaypitana tsay gapra cashganpita aliyashga runata pushapäcorgan fariseo runacunaman.  
\v 14-15 Sábado jamay junag aliyashga captinmi fariseo runacuna payta tapupäcorgan imanogpa aliyashgantapis. Tapuptinmi caynog nergan: “Juc runami nawëta mituwan lushipämargan. Tsay lushipämashgan mituta maylacuptënami nawë ricaycanna, tayta.” 
\p  
\v 16 Tsaymi waquin fariseo runacuna caynog nipäcorgan: “Tsay aliyätsishogniqui runaga manami Tayta Dios cachamushgantsu canman. Tayta Dios cachamushgan runa carga sábado jamay junagchöga manami aliyätsinmantsu pitapis.” 
\p Tsaycho caycag waquin runacunanami caynog nipäcorgan: “Tayta Dios mana cachamushga captenga ¿imanogpatag aliyätsinman cargan tsay runata?” 
\p  
\v 17 Tsauraga yapay tapupäcorgan gapra cashganpita aliyashga runata: “Gamga ¿pï cashgantatag yarpanqui tsay aliyätsishogniqui runapäga?” 
\p Tsaynog tapupäcuptinmi caynog nergan: “Nogaga yarpä Tayta Diosnintsipa profëtan cashgantami.” 
\p  
\v 18 Tsaynog niptinpis Israel runacunapa autoridänincunaga manami criyipäcorgantsu rasunpa gapra cashganta. Tsaymi mamanta y taytanta gayaycatsimur tapupäcorgan caynog nir:  
\v 19 “¿Cay runa tsuriquicu? ¿Rasunpacu gapra yurergan? ¿Imanogpatag aliyashga?” 
\p  
\v 20 Tsauraga maman y taytan caynog nipäcorgan: “Au, payga tsurëmi. Rasunpami yurishganpita-patsa gapra cashga.  
\v 21 Itsanga manami musyapäcötsu imanogpa aliyashgantapis ni pï aliyätsishgantapis. Payga caycan auquis runanami. Quiquinta tapupäcuy.” 
\p  
\v 22 Maman y taytan tsaynog nipäcorgan autoridäcunata mantsacushpanmi. Autoridäcunaga wilanacushganami caycargan mayganpis: “Jesusga Tayta Dios cachamushgan Cristumi” neg cagtaga sinagogapita gargunanpag.\f + \fr 9:22 \ft Sinagogapita autoridäcuna pitapis gargapäcog imaypis manana cutinanpagmi. Tsaymi manana cutegnatsu Tayta Diosta adorananpag ni runacuna sesionta ruraptin parlananpagpis.\f* 
\v 23 Tsayta mantsacurmi maman y taytan caynog nipäcorgan: “Payga auquis runanami. Quiquinta tapupäcuy.” 
\p  
\v 24 Tsauraga gapra cashganpita aliyashga runata autoridäcuna yapay gayatsimorgan caynog nir tapupäcunanpag: “Tayta Dios ricaycäshunquimi. Rasun cagta wilapäcamay. Musyapäcömi tsay aliyätsishogniqui runataga Tayta Dios mana cachamushganta.” 
\p  
\v 25 Tsauraga tsay runa caynog nergan: “Nogaga manami musyätsu Tayta Dios cachamushganta o mana cachamushgantapis. Itsanga musyä gapra cashgäpita aliyätsimashgantami.” 
\p  
\v 26 Tsaynog niptin yapay tapupäcorgan: “¿Imatatag rurashga aliyätsishunayquipag?” 
\p  
\v 27 Niptinmi caynog nergan: “Maynami gamcunata wilashcä. Wilaptëpis gamcunaga manami criyimanquitsu. ¿Imanirtag yaparir yaparir tsaynog tapupäcamanqui? ¿Gamcunapis payta gatiraytacu munarcaycanqui?” 
\p  
\v 28 Tsaynog niptinmi rabiacushpan nipäcorgan: “Gamchari paypa discïpulonga caycanqui. Nogacunaga Moisés yachatsishgancunatami cäsucärë.  
\v 29 Musyapäcömi Moisesta Tayta Dios mandamientuncunata entregashganta. Tsay aliyätsishogniqui runataga, jutsasapa captin, Tayta Dios manami imatapis musyatsishgatsu.” 
\p  
\v 30 Tsaynog niptinmi gapra cashganpita aliyashga runa caynog nergan: “¿Imanogtag tsayga? Tsay runa nawëta aliyaycätsimaptenga ¿imanirtag mana tantyapäcunquitsu Tayta Dios cachamushganta?  
\v 31 Milagruta rurananpäga Tayta Dios manami imaypis jutsasapacunata yanapantsu, sinöga payta adorar munashgannog cawagcunalatami.  
\v 32 Manami imaypis mayashcantsitsu yurishganpita-patsa gapra runata pipis aliyätsishganta.  
\v 33 Tayta Dios mana yanapaptenga tsay runa manami imanogpapis aliyätsimanmantsu cargan.” 
\p  
\v 34 Tsaynog niptinmi autoridäcuna nipäcorgan: “¡Gamga jutsasapa carmi gapra yurishcanqui! ¡Tsaynog caycarga manami imatapis nogacunata yachatsimanquimantsu!” 
\p Tsaynog nipäcushpanmi sinagogapita tsay runata gargapäcorgan imaypis manana cutinanpag. 
\s1 Jesucristuta chasquicogcuna salvashga cananpag cashgan 
\p  
\v 35 Tsay aliyätsishgan runata sinagogapita gargushgantami Jesús musyargan. Tsaymi paywan tincurcur nergan: “¿Tayta Dios cachamushgan runaman yäracunquicu?” 
\p  
\v 36 Niptin tsay runa caynog nergan: “Reguerga payman yäracömanmi, tayta.” 
\p  
\v 37 Tsauraga Jesús nergan: “Tayta Dios cachamushgan runawanga maynami tincushcanqui. Tsay runaga nogami caycä.” 
\p  
\v 38 Tsaynog niptinmi Jesuspa naupanman gongurpacuycur caynog nergan: “Gamman yäracömi, tayta.” 
\p  
\v 39 Tsaynog niptinmi Jesús nergan: “Nogaga cay patsaman shamushcä mana tantyacogcunata tantyatsinäpag y yachag-tucogcunata upatacätsinäpagmi.” 
\p  
\v 40 Tsaynog nishganta mayapäcushpanmi tsaycho caycag waquin fariseo runacuna nipäcorgan: “¿Nogacunapis upatacashga cashgätacu yarpanqui?” 
\p  
\v 41 Tsaynog niptin Jesús nergan: “Gapra runa chasquicamashgannog gamcunapis chasquicamaptiquega Tayta Dios jutsayquicunata perdonashunquimanmi. ‘Salvashganami caycä’ niycarpis nogata mana chasquicamaptiquega Tayta Dios manami perdonashunquipagtsu.” 
\c 10  
\s1 Uysha mitsicogman Jesucristo tincutsicushgan 
\p  
\v 1 Mastapis Jesús caynog nergan: “Uysha cunchaman puncupa mana yaycog cäga suwami caycan.  
\v 2 Cuncha puncupa yaycog cagmi itsanga uyshapa duëñun caycan.  
\v 3 Musyashgantsinogpis cuncha puncuta quichapaptin uyshapa duëñonga jutinpa jutinpa gayan uyshancunata.\f + \fr 10:3 \ft Cay patsacho Jesús purinan witsanga runacunapa uyshan juc cunchalacho talucashgami punupäcog. Tsaychömi uysha täpag runa puncuta quichapaptin uyshapa duëñun uyshancunata jutinpa jutinpa gayag.\f* Tsaynog gayashganta mayashpanmi cunchapita uyshancuna yargapäcamun.  
\v 4 Lapan yargamurnami duëñunpa guepanta aywapäcun, duëñunta reguishpan.  
\v 5 Jäpa captenga manami gatirantsu. Gatiränanpa trucanga gueshpirmi aywacärin.” 
\p  
\v 6 Tincutsiypa tsaynog Jesús yachatsiptinmi tsaycho cag runacuna mana tantyapäcorgantsu tsaynog tincutsir imata yachaycätsishgantapis.  
\v 7 Tsauraga Jesús caynog nergan: “Nogaga caycä uysha cuncha puncunogmi.  
\v 8-9 Tsaymi cuncha puncupa uyshacuna yaycushgannog nogata chasquicamag runacuna gloriaman yaycapäcongapag. Uyshacuna ali guewacho weray weray cashgannogmi nogata chasquicamagcuna ali cawayta tarengapag. Manarag shamuptë waquin runacuna lutanta yachatsishpan puripäcorgan caynog nir: ‘Nogatami Tayta Dios cachamashga wilacuyninta wilacunäpag.’ Tsaynog yachatsiptinpis Tayta Diosman rasunpa yäracogcuna paycunata manami chasquicärergantsu.  
\v 10 Suwaga shamun suwacunanpag, wanutsinanpag y ushacätsinanpagmi. Nogami itsanga shamushcä chasquicamag runacuna imayyagpis cushishgala cawapäcunanpag. 
\p  
\v 11 “Tsaynogpis uyshanta ali mitseg runanogmi caycä. Uyshancunata wanuy caway mitsegnin salvashgannogmi\f + \fr 10:11 \ft Jesucristo cawashgan witsan uysha mitsegcuna uyshancunata washargan atogpita, löbupita, leonpita y ösupitapis.\f* nogapis uyshäcunata salvanä-raycu wanushagpag.  
\v 12 Pägu-raycula mitsipacog cäga löbu shamuptin gueshpirmi aywacun. Tsaynog aywacun duëñun mana cashpanmi. Tsauraga löbu gaticachaptin uyshacuna gueshpir matsipa matsirmi may-tsaypapis aywacärin.  
\v 13 Tsaynog mitsipacog cäga uyshacuna elgaptinpis manami imapis gocuntsu. 
\p  
\v 14-15 “Nogaga rasunpa ali mitseg runanogmi caycä. Tsaymi Taytäta reguishgänog y pay nogata reguimashgannog nogapis uyshäcunata reguë y uyshäcunapis nogata reguiman. Tsaynogpis uyshäcuna-raycumi wanushagpag.  
\v 16 Manami caylachötsu uyshäcuna caycan, sinöga may-tsaychöpis caycanmi. Paycunapis nishgäcunata mayar cäsucärimangami. Tsaymi paycunatapis shuntamushag juc cunchalachöna cananpag. Tsaynogpis juclaylanami uysha mitsegnin cangapag. 
\p  
\v 17 “Taytäta cäsucur uyshäcuna-raycumi wanushag. Nircurnami cawarimushagpag. Tsaynog cäsucog captëmi Taytä cushicun.  
\v 18 Noga munayniyogmi caycä wanunäpag y cawarimunäpagpis. Tsaymi quiquë mana munaptëga pipis mana wanutsimanmantsu. Tsaynog captinpis Taytä nimashgannogmi wanushag y wanushgäpita cawarimushag.” 
\p  
\v 19 Jesús tsaynog parlaptinmi Israel runacunapa waquin autoridänincuna yarpargan rasun cagta niycashganta y waquin cagna yarpargan quiquinpa yarpaynilanpita parlaycashganta.  
\v 20 Tsaymi waquin nipäcorgan: “Payta demonio löcutaycätsiptenga ¿imapagtag cäsucushun?” 
\p  
\v 21 Y waquin cagnami nipäcorgan: “Demonio löcutätsishga captenga manami tsaynog parlanmantsu. Tsaynogpis gapra runata manami aliyätsinmantsu cargan.” 
\s1 Runacuna Jesucristuta mana chasquicushgan 
\p  
\v 22-23 Diciembri quilla templupa aniversariuncho fiestata rurapäcuptinmi templucho Jesús puriycargan Salomón nishgan alarcho.  
\v 24 Tsaychömi Israel runacunapa autoridänincuna Jesusta tapupäcorgan: “¿Imayyagtag shuyäshayqui rasun cagta wilapäcamänayquipag? Tayta Dios cachamushgan Cristo cashgayquita o mana cashgayquitapis jucla wilapäcamay.” 
\p  
\v 25 Tsaynog nipäcuptinmi Jesús nergan: “Maynami gamcunata wilashcä. Wilaptëpis manami criyipäcamanquitsu. Taytäpa munayninwan milagrucunata ruraycaptëpis manami criyipäcamanquitsu.  
\v 26 Gamcunaga mana criyipäcamanquitsu uyshäcuna mana cashpayquimi. 
\p  
\v 27 “Uyshäcunami itsanga pï cashgätapis tantyashpan cäsucaman. Tsaynogpis reguëmi uyshäcuna maygan maygan cashganta.  
\v 28 Nogata chasquicamashganpitami Tayta Diospa naupancho imayyagpis cawangapag. Maquëcho captinnaga manami pipis guechumanganatsu.  
\v 29 Maquëcho caycarga Taytäpa maquinchöpis caycanmi. Taytä lapanpagpis munayniyog captinmi diablupis ni demoniupis ni pipis paypa maquinpita guechongatsu.  
\v 30 Taytäwan nogaga juclaylami caycä.” 
\p  
\v 31 Tsaynog niptinmi tsay autoridäcuna Jesusta sagmayta munapäcorgan.  
\v 32 Tsauraga Jesús nergan: “Gamcuna ricashcanquimi atsca milagrucunata Taytäpa munayninwan rurashgäta. ¿Tsaynog alita rurashgäpitacu sagmayta munaycämanqui?” 
\p  
\v 33 Tsauraga tsay runacuna nipäcorgan: “Manami alita rurashgayquipitatsu sagmayta munapäcö, sinöga runala caycar Dios-tucuycashgayquipitami.” 
\p  
\v 34 Tsaynog nipäcuptin Jesús nergan: “Tayta Diosnintsipa palabrancho caynogmi niycan: ‘Gamcunaga dioscunami carcaycanqui.’\f + \fr 10:34 \ft Dios cashganta unay runacuna pipagpis nergan mandag cashganpitami. Tsaypita masta musyanayquipag liyinqui Salmo 82.6.\f* 
\v 35-36 Musyapäcunquimi Tayta Diospa palabrancho lapanpis rasun cagla cashganta. Tsaymi Diospa wilacuyninta unay mayagcunapag: ‘Gamcunaga dioscunami carcaycanqui’ niycaptenga ¿imanirtag: ‘Diospa tsurinmi caycä’ niptë yarpapäcunqui lutanta niycashgäta? Quiquin Tayta Diosnintsimi cay patsaman cachamashga. 
\p  
\v 37 “Milagruta rurashgäcuna Taytä munashgannog mana captenga ama criyipäcamaytsu: ‘Diospa tsurinmi caycä’ niptëpis.  
\v 38 Nishgäcunata mana criyirpis milagruta rurashgäcunata ricaycarga tantyacäriy Taytäwan tsay yarpayla cashgäta.” 
\p  
\v 39 Tsaynog nishganpitami Jesusta yapay prësu tsaritsiyta munargan. Tsaynog munaptinpis Jesús tsaypita aywacorgan.  
\v 40 Nircurnami Jordán mayu tsimpanman Jesús cutergan. Tsaychömi naupata Juan Bautista bautizargan runacunata.  
\v 41 Jesús tsaycho cashganta musyarmi tsayman atsca runacuna aywargan. Paycuna caynogmi nipäcorgan: “Ima milagrutapis Juan Bautista manami rurashgatsu. Tsaynog captinpis Jesuspita lapan nishgancunaga rasun caglami caycan.” 
\p  
\v 42 Tsaynog nirmi atsca runacuna criyipäcorgan Tayta Dios cachamushgan Cristo cashganta. 
\c 11  
\s1 Lázaro wanushgan 
\p  
\v 1 Betania marcachömi targan juc runa Lázaro jutiyog. Paymi antsa gueshyaycargan. Paypa panincunami cargan María y Marta.  
\v 2 (Mariami Jesuspa chaquinman perfümita winaparcur agtsanwan pitsapargan.)\f + \fr 11:2 \ft Tsaypita musyanayquipag liyinqui San Juan 12.1-8.\f* 
\v 3 Lázaro antsa gueshyaptinmi panincuna juc runata Jesusman cachacorgan: “Cuyanacushgayqui Läzarumi pasaypa antsa caycan, tayta” nir wilananpag. 
\p  
\v 4 Tsaynog wilaptinmi Jesús caynog nergan: “Läzarutaga tsay gueshya tsarishga manami wanushgalancho quëdananpagtsu, sinöga noga cawaritsimuptë munayniyog cashgäta runacuna tantyacunanpagmi.” 
\p  
\v 5-7 Läzaruwan y panincunawan cuyanacurpis Jesús manami juclaga aywargantsu. Tsaypa trucanga pasaypa antsa cashganta wilaycaptinpis cashgan caglachömi ishcay junag goyargan. Tsaypitanami discïpuluncunata nergan: “Acu cutishun Judea provinciapa.” 
\p  
\v 8 Tsauraga discïpuluncuna caynog nipäcorgan: “Ganyancunaragchag tsaycho cag runacuna sagmaypa wanutsiyta munapäcushushcanqui, tayta. ¿Tsaynog caycaptincu tsayman yapay cutiyta munaycanqui?” 
\p  
\v 9-10 Tsauraga Jesús caynog nergan: “Ama mantsacäriytsu. Wanutsimänanpäga manami hörä chämunragtsu. Musyashgantsinogpis tsacaypa puregcunalami mantsacun. Junagpa puregcunaga manami mantsacuntsu. Tsaynoglami wanutsimänanpag hörä manarag chämuptin gamcunaga ama mantsacäriytsu.” 
\p  
\v 11 Nircurnami Jesús discïpuluncunata nergan: “Cuyashgantsi Läzaroga punucashgalami caycan. Acu aywashun ricchatsinantsipag.” 
\p  
\v 12 Tsaynog niptinmi discïpuluncuna caynog nergan: “Ali punuyta tariptinmi musyantsi aliyänanpag cashganta, tayta.” 
\p  
\v 13 Lázaro punucashga cashganta nirpis wanushga cashgantami Jesús tumatsipaylapa nergan. Tsaymi discïpuluncunaga mana tantyar punucashga caycashgalanta yarpargan.  
\v 14 Tsaynog yarpaptinmi Jesús discïpuluncunata caynog nergan: “Läzaroga wanushgami caycan.  
\v 15 Wanushganpita cawaritsimuptëmi gamcuna más tantyapäcunquipag Tayta Dios cachamashganta. Tsaymi cushicö Lázaro cashgan cagcho mana cashgäpita. Pay cagman acu aywashun.” 
\p  
\v 16 Tsauraga Milïshu nipäcushgan Tomasmi discípulu mayincunata caynog nergan: “Tsaynog captenga nogantsipis wanunantsipag aywashun.” 
\s1 Wanushcunata cawaritsimunanpag Jesucristo munayniyog cashgan 
\p  
\v 17 Betaniaman chayarnami Jesús musyargan chuscu junagna Lázaro pamparaycashganta.  
\v 18-19 Jerusalenpita Betaniaman pulan lëwanogla captinmi atsca runacuna aywapäcorgan Martata y Mariata yanagänanpag.  
\v 20 “Jesusmi aywaycämun” negta mayarmi Marta aywargan taripänanpag. Mariami itsanga wayicho quëdacorgan.  
\v 21 Jesuswan tincurmi Marta caynog nergan: “Caycho captiquega turë manami wanunmantsu cargan, tayta.  
\v 22 Imanog captinpis gammanmi imaypis yäracö. Noga musyämi imata manacuptiquipis Tayta Dios mayashushgayquita.” 
\p  
\v 23 Tsaynog niptinmi Jesús nergan: “Turiqui cawarimongami.” 
\p  
\v 24 Tsauraga Marta caynog nergan: “Au, musyämi juicio final junag wanushcuna cawarimuptin turëpis cawarimunanpag cashganta, tayta.” 
\p  
\v 25-26 Niptinmi Jesús nergan: “Nogami cawaritsimö wanushcunata. Nogata chasquicamag cagtaga wanuptinpis cawaritsimushagmi gloriacho imayyagpis cawananpag. ¿Tsayta criyinquicu?” 
\p  
\v 27 Tsaynog niptinmi Marta nergan: “Au, tayta. Noga criyëmi. Gammi Tayta Diospa tsurin caycanqui. Tsaynogpis caycanqui Tayta Dios cachamushgan Cristumi.” 
\s1 Läzarupag Jesucristo wagashgan 
\p  
\v 28 Tsaynog nircushpanmi Marta cutergan nanan María cagman paypis Jesuswan tincog aywananpag. Chayaycushpanna gayaycur caynog wilargan: “Jesusmi chämushga. Paymi gayaycäshunqui.” 
\p  
\v 29 Tsaynog niptin María jucla aywargan.  
\v 30 Jesús manaragmi marcaman chayarganragtsu, sinöga Martawan tincushgalanchöragmi caycargan.  
\v 31 Wayipita María jucla yargogta ricapäcushpanmi payta yanagag runacuna guepanta aywapäcorgan: “Turin pamparaycashganmanchari aywaycan wagananpag” nishpan. 
\p  
\v 32 Tsauraga Jesús cagman María chayaycurmi naupanman gongurpacuycur nergan: “Gam caycho captiquega manami turë wanunmantsu cargan, tayta.” 
\p  
\v 33 Tsauraga Mariata y yanagagnin runacunatapis wagaycagta ricarmi Jesuspis fiyupa laquicorgan.  
\v 34 Tsaymi paycunata taporgan: “¿Mayninchötag pamparaycan?” 
\p Tapuptinmi nipäcorgan: “Maynincho pamparaycashgantapis ricanayquipag aywashun, tayta.” 
\p  
\v 35 Tsauraga pamparashgan cagman aywaycarmi Jesuspis laquicushpan Läzarupag wagargan.  
\v 36 Tsaymi waquin runacuna caynog nipäcorgan: “Ricay, pasaypachari cuyanacorgan Läzaruwan.” 
\p  
\v 37 Waquincunami itsanga nipäcorgan: “Gapra runatapis aliyaycätserga ¿manatsurag Läzarutapis aliyätsinman cargan mana wanunanpag?” 
\s1 Lázaro cawarimushgan 
\p  
\v 38 Pasaypa laquishgami Jesús chayargan Lázaro pamparashgan cagman. Tsay pamparashgan sepultüraga cargan gagacho uchcushgami. Puncunnami tsaparargan jatun rumiwan.  
\v 39 Tsayman chayaycurmi Jesús caynog nergan: “Tsaparaycag rumita wititsipäcuy.” 
\p Tsaynog niptinmi Läzarupa panin Marta nergan: “Chuscu junagnami pamparaycan, tayta. Cananyäga fiyupanachari asyaycan.” 
\p  
\v 40 Tsaynog niptin Jesús nergan: “¿Manacu nishcä nogaman yäracamaptiquega turiquita cawaritsimunäpag cashganta?” 
\p  
\v 41-42 Tsauraga tsaparaycag rumita witircatsiptinnami jana patsata ricärir Jesús caynog nergan: “Manacushgäta imaypis mayamashgayquipitami gamta agradëcicamö, papá. Yanapamashgayquita ricarmi caycho carcaycag runacuna tantyapäcongapag gam cachamashgayquita.” 
\p  
\v 43 Nircushpannami Jesús fuertipa caynog nergan: “¡Lázaro, yargamuy!” 
\p  
\v 44 Tsaynog niptinmi wanushga jitaraycashganpita cawarircamur Lázaro yargamorgan uman wancushga y maquin chaquin wancushga. Yargaramuptinnami Jesús nergan: “Purinanpag pascapäcuy.” 
\s1 Jesucristuta wanutsinanpag mandag cüracuna wilanacushgan 
\r (Mateo 26.1-5; Marcos 14.1-2; Lucas 22.1-2) 
\p  
\v 45 Tsauraga Läzaruta cawaritsimushganta ricaycurmi Mariata yanagag runacuna atscag criyipäcorgan Jesusta Tayta Dios cachamushganta.  
\v 46 Waquin cagnami fariseo runacunaman aywaycur wilapargan Läzaruta cawaritsimuptin atsca runacuna payman criyiycashganta.  
\v 47 Tsayta mayaycurmi mandag cüracuna y fariseo runacuna Israel runacunapa autoridänincunata gayaycatsir caynog nipäcorgan: “Milagrucunata ruraptin aläpanami runacuna criyiycan Dios cachamushgan Cristo cashganta. ¿Imatatag rurashun tsay runata?  
\v 48 Payta prësu mana tsaritsiptintsega milagro rurashgancunata ricar lapan runacunami munapäconga nacionnintsipa mandagnin rey cananta. Tsayta mayaycurmi Romacho mandag emperador fiyupa rabiacushpan soldäduncunata cachamonga templuntsita juchutsinanpag y lapantsitapis wanutsimänantsipag.” 
\p  
\v 49 Tsaynog nipäcuptin más mandag cüra Caifás caynog nergan: “¡Gamcunaga manami imatapis tantyapäcunquitsu!  
\v 50 Templuntsita mana juchutsinanpag y mana wanutsimänantsipag tsay runala wanutsun. Tsaynogpami lapantsipis salvacushunpag.” 
\p  
\v 51-52 “Tsay runala wanutsun lapantsi salvacunantsipag” nir Caifás nergan Roma runacuna Israel runacunata wanutsinanta mana munarmi. Payga manami tantyargantsu jutsantsicunapita wanur Jesús salvamänantsipag cashganta. Mana tantyaptinpis tsaynog parlananpag Tayta Dios yarpätsergan más mandag cüra tsay wata captinmi. Caifás nishgannoglami Jesús wanorgan Israel runacunata y mana Israel runacunatapis salvananpag.  
\v 53 Tsauraga tsay junagpitanami autoridäcuna wilanacärergan Jesusta wanutsinanpag. 
\p  
\v 54 Tsayta musyarmi Israel runacunapa autoridänincunapita pacaylapana Jesús purergan. Tsaymi Judea provinciapita Jesús discïpuluncunawan aywacorgan Efraín nishgan marcaman tsaycho goyänanpag. Tsay marcaga chunyag jirca cercalanchömi caycan.  
\v 55 Tsay junagcuna Pascua aniversario galaycunanpagna caycaptinmi marcancunapita atsca runacuna Jerusalenman aywapäcorgan Tayta Dios nishgannog tsay aniversariupag camaricog.  
\v 56 Templo patiuchönami runacuna caynog nergan: “Gamcunaga ¿imatatag yarpapäcunqui? ¿Aniversariupag Jesús shamongatsurag o manatsurag?” 
\p  
\v 57 Fariseo runacunawan mandag cüracuna maynami runacunata caynog nipäcorgan: “Jesusta maychöpis ricashpayquega jucla wilapäcamanqui prësu tsaritsipäcunäpag.” 
\c 12  
\s1 Jesucristupa chaquinman perfümita María winapashgan 
\r (Mateo 26.6-13; Marcos 14.3-9) 
\p  
\v 1 Pascua aniversariupag sogta junag pishiycaptinmi Jesús aywargan Betania marcaman. Tsaychömi wanushganpita cawaritsimushgan Lázaro targan.  
\v 2 Tsayman Jesús chayashganpita cushicurmi Läzarupa panincuna cënayta yanucärergan paywan micapäcunanpag. Waquin runacunawan mësaman Jesús jamacuptinmi Läzarupis jamacorgan paycunawan micunanpag. Tsaymanmi panin Marta paycunata garargan. 
\p  
\v 3 Tsaycho micurcaycaptinmi botëllawan María apamorgan nardu jachapita rurashga chanin cuestag perfümita. Nircurmi Jesuspa chaquinman winaparcur agtsanwan sëcapargan.\f + \fr 12:3 \ft Tsay witsanmi runacuna pampaman weguycur micapäcog. Tsaynog micuptinmi Jesuspa chaquinta María agtsanwan sëcapargan.\f* Tsay perfümimi wayi junta asyargan.\f + \fr 12:3 \ft Waquin runacuna nipäcun: “Wayi junta mushcorgan.”\f* 
\v 4 Tsauraga Jesusta entregananpag cag discïpulun Judas Iscariote caynog nergan:  
\v 5 “¿Imanirtag cay perfümita perdiycätsin? Tsaypa trucanga ranticushwan cargan juc wata arupacur gänashgantsichönog. Nircur tsay guellaywanna wactsacunata yanapashwan cargan.” 
\p  
\v 6 Judasmi shuntapäcushgan guellay tsararag cargan. Tsaynog nergan manami wactsacunata yanapayta munartsu, sinöga quiquinpag guellayta raquinan cashgami.  
\v 7 Tsauraga Jesús nergan: “Winapämashganpita ama jamurpaytsu. Tsay perfümitaga churarätsergan manaragpis wanuptë winapämänanpagmi.  
\v 8 Wactsacunaga yanapanayquipag imaypis caycangami. Nogaga mananami gamcunawan cashagpagnatsu.” 
\s1 Läzarutapis wanutsiyta munapäcushgan 
\p  
\v 9 Betania marcacho Jesús caycashganta musyarmi atsca runacuna tsayman aywapäcorgan. Manami Jesusta ricaglatsu aywapäcorgan, sinöga Lázaro cawarimushganta ricananpagwanmi aywapäcorgan.  
\v 10-11 Läzaruta cawaritsimushganpita Jesusman atsca runacuna criyiptinmi mandag cüracuna Läzarutapis wanutsiyta munapäcorgan. 
\s1 Jerusalenman Jesucristo yaycuptin runacuna alabashgan 
\r (Mateo 21.1-11; Marcos 11.1-11; Lucas 19.28-40) 
\p  
\v 12-13 Wara tuta runacuna musyapäcorgan Jerusalenman Jesús aywaycashganta. Tsaymi Pascua aniversariuman aywag atsca runacuna, palmacunata muturcur, apapäcorgan Jesusta chasquicärinanpag.\f + \fr 12:12-13 \ft Tsay witsan costumbri cashgannog marcaman juc rey yaycuptin runacuna cushishga chasquicorga jacuncunata, punchuncunata y palmatapis caminuman mashtapag.\f* Jesús chayaptinna caynog nipäcorgan: “¡Tayta Diosnintsi cachamushgan mandamagnintsi caychönami caycan! ¡Paymi mandamagnintsi rey caycan!”\x + \xo 12:12-13 \xt Salmo 118.25-26; Sofonías 3.15\x* 
\p  
\v 14 Tayta Diosnintsipa palabrancho escribiraycashgannoglami manta orgu bürrun muntashga Jerusalenman Jesús chayargan. Tsay escribiraycashganga caynogmi niycan: 
\q1  
\v 15 “Jerusalén marcacho tag runacuna, 
\q1 ricapäcuy humildi runanogla mandagniqui rey manta bürrun muntashga aywaycämogta.”\x + \xo 12:15 \xt Zacarías 9.9\x* 
\m  
\v 16 Jerusalenman bürrun muntashga Jesús chayaptinmi discïpuluncuna mana tantyapäcorgantsu imanir tsaynog ruraycashgantapis. Wanushganpita cawarircamuptinragmi tantyapäcorgan Jesús rurashgancuna Tayta Diospa palabrancho nishgannogla caycashganta. 
\p  
\v 17-18 Läzaruta cawaritsimushganta musyashpanmi atsca runacuna cushishga Jesusta taripag shapäcamorgan. Pay cawaritsimushganta ricag runacunapis Tayta Diosta alabaraycar aywarcaycargan. Nänipa aywashpanmi pï-maytapis tincushgan cagta wilapargan Läzaruta cawaritsimushganta. 
\p  
\v 19 Jesusman atsca runacuna criyishganta ricarmi fariseo runacuna caynog nipäcorgan: “Cananga ¿imatatag rurashun? ¡Lapan runacunami payman criyiycan!” 
\s1 Mana Israel runacuna Jesucristuwan parlayta munashgan 
\p  
\v 20 Pascua aniversario captinmi may-tsay nacioncunapitapis Jerusalenman aywapäcorgan mana Israel runacunapis.  
\v 21 Paycunapita waquin runacunami Felipita ruwacärergan: “Jesusta reguiycatsilämay, tayta” nir. (Felipega cargan Galilea provinciacho Betsaida marcapitami.) 
\p  
\v 22 Tsaynog manacäriptinmi Felipe aywaycur Andresta wilargan. Nircurnami ishcan aywaycur Jesusta wilargan mana Israel runacuna paywan tincuyta munarcaycashganta.  
\v 23 Wilaptinmi Jesús caynog nergan: “\nd Noga\nd* wanunäpag cag höra chaycämunnami.  
\v 24 Shumag tantyacäriy. Musyashgantsinogpis trïguta murur mana pampaptintsega manami winamuntsu. Pampaptintsimi itsanga winamur ali wayun. Tsaynoglami noga mana wanuptë pipis mana salvacongatsu. Wanuptëmi itsanga atsca runacuna salvacärengapag. 
\p  
\v 25 “Tayta Diosta cäsucunanpa trucan quiquin munashgannog cawacuyta munagcunaga manami pipis gloriaman chayangatsu. Tayta Dios munashgannog cawag cagcunami itsanga gloriaman chayar imayyagpis cawapäcongapag.  
\v 26 Pipis discïpulö cayta munarga noga cawashgänog cawatsun. Imanog nacarpis mana ajayaypa gatirämätsun. Tsaynog gatirämagcunataga Taytä cushishgalami chasquengapag. 
\s1 Wanunanpag cashganta Jesucristo wilacushgan 
\p  
\v 27 “Cananga fiyupa laquishgami caycä. Tsaynog laquishga caycarpis manami Taytäta manacömantsu wanunäpag cashganpita tsapämänanpag. Tsaynog wanunäpagmi cay patsaman shamushcä.” 
\p  
\v 28 Tsaynog nishpanmi Tayta Diosta manacorgan caynog nir: “Munayniyog cashgayquita runacuna tantyacunanpag gam munashgayquinog lapanpis cayculätsun, papá.” 
\p Tsaynog manacuptinmi jana patsapita Tayta Dios caynog nimorgan: “Manacamashgayquita imaypis rurashgänoglami cananpis rurashag.” 
\p  
\v 29 Tsayta mayarmi tsaycho cag waquin runacuna: “¡Räyumi cashga!” nipäcorgan. Waquincunanami: “¡Angilmi rimamushga!” nipäcorgan. 
\p  
\v 30 Tsauraga Jesús caynog nergan: “Manami gamcuna nishgayquinogtsu caycan. Tayta Diosmi tsaynog parlamushga nogaman yäracamänayquipag.  
\v 31 Runacunata Tayta Diosnintsi juzgananpag cag höra chayaycämunnami. Tsaynogmi runacunata munaynincho tsararag diablupis vincishga cananpag höran chämongana.  
\v 32 Tsaymi crucificamashganpita cawarircamur Israel runacunata y mana Israel runacunatapis tantyatsishag nogaman yäracamänanpag.” 
\p  
\v 33 Tsaynog nirmi Jesús tantyatsergan crucificaypa wanutsishga cananpag cashganta.  
\v 34 Tsaymi runacuna caynog nipäcorgan: “Tayta Diosnintsipa palabranchöga niycan salvamagnintsi Cristo imayyagpis cawananpag cashgantami. Tsauraga ¿imanirtag niycanqui wanunayquipag cashganta? Tsaynog captenga ¿rasunpacu Cristo caycanqui?” 
\p  
\v 35 Tsaynog niptinmi Jesús caynog nergan: “Au, Tayta Dios cachamashgan Cristumi caycä. Tsaynog captinpis walca junaglanami gamcunawan cashagpag. Tsaymi gamcunawan caycashgäyag jutsayquicunata cacharir yachatsishgäcunata chasquicäriy. Chasquicorga wanutsimaptinpis Tayta Diospa naupanman chayanquipagmi. Jutsayquicunata mana cacharerga manami imanogpapis paypa naupanman chayanquipagtsu.  
\v 36 Tsaynog caycaptenga yachatsishgäcunata chasquicäriy. Tsaynogpami gamcunapis Tayta Diospa wamrancuna canquipag.” 
\p Tsaynog nircushpanmi Jesús aywacorgan. Tsaynog aywacuptinnami runacuna mana musyapäcorgantsu maypa aywacushgantapis. 
\s1 Dios cachamushgan Cristo cashganta runacuna mana criyishgan 
\p  
\v 37 Atsca milagrucunata Jesús ruraycashganta ricarpis runacuna manami criyipäcorgantsu Tayta Dios cachamushgan Cristo cashganta.  
\v 38 Tsaynog mana criyinanpag cashganpitami Tayta Diosnintsipa profëtan Isaías unay escribergan caynog nir: 
\q1 “Tayta Dios, wilacuyniquita wilacuptëpis runacuna manami chasquicuntsu. 
\q1 Milagrucunata ricarpis manami criyipäcuntsu.”\x + \xo 12:38 \xt Isaías 53.1\x* 
\m  
\v 39 Mastapis paycunapag Isaías caynogmi escribergan: 
\q1  
\v 40 “Tayta Diosmi yarpayninta upatacätsergan wilacuyninta mana tantyapäcunanpag. 
\q1 Tsaynogmi shonguntapis chucruyätsergan payman mana yäracärinanpag. 
\q1 Tsaymi payta mana chasquicuntsu jutsancunapita perdonashga cananpag.”\x + \xo 12:40 \xt Isaías 6.10\x* 
\m  
\v 41 Isaías tsaynog escribergan runacuna Jesusta mana chasquicärinanpag cashganta musyarmi. Paytami Tayta Diosnintsi ricatsergan Jesucristo gloriacho munayniyog caycagta.\f + \fr 12:41 \ft Isaías gloriacho ricashgancunata musyanayquipag liyinqui Isaías 6-ta.\f* 
\p  
\v 42 Jesucristuta waquin Israel runacuna mana chasquicuptinpis waquin cag Israel runacunami itsanga criyipäcorgan Tayta Dios cachamushgan Cristo cashganta. Tsaynoglami Israel autoridäcunapis waquenga criyipäcorgan Tayta Dios cachamushgan Cristo cashganta. Tsaynog criyipäcurpis sinagogapita fariseo autoridäcuna gargunanta mantsacushpanmi Jesusman yäracushganta mana wilacorgantsu.  
\v 43 Tayta Diospita ali ricashga cananpa trucanga paycunaga más munapäcorgan runacunalapita ali ricashga caytami. 
\s1 Jesucristuta chasquicogcuna Tayta Diostapis chasquishgan 
\p  
\v 44 Tsaypitana fuertipa Jesús caynog nergan: “Nogata chasquicamag cäga cachamagnë Taytätapis chasquicuycanmi.  
\v 45 Tsaynogpis nogata reguimag cäga cachamagnë Taytätapis reguiycanmi.  
\v 46 Chasquicamagcuna Tayta Diosta reguir tsacäpacushganog mana cananpagmi cay patsaman shamushcä. Tsaymi runacunapag noga atsquinog caycä. 
\p  
\v 47-48 “Manami runacunata juzganäpagtsu cay patsaman shamushcä, sinöga jutsancunata perdonar salvanäpagmi. Tsaynog captinpis nishgäcunata mana cäsucamagcunaga manami perdonashgatsu canga, sinöga juicio final junag infiernuman gaycushgami cangapag. 
\p  
\v 49 “Manami quiquiläpa yarpayniläpitatsu wilacuycä, sinöga Taytä nimashgancunalatami wilacuycä. Paymi imata wilacunäpagpis tantyatsimashga.  
\v 50 Tsaynog wilacuptëmi runacuna chasquicur gloriaman chayangapag. Tsaymi Taytä nimashgannogla imaypis wilacuycä.” 
\c 13  
\s1 Discïpuluncunapa chaquinta Jesucristo maylapashgan 
\p  
\v 1-5 Jesusga musyarganmi paypa munayninman lapantapis Tayta Dios churamushganta. Tsaynogpis musyarganmi cay patsapita taytan cagman cuticunanpag caycashganta. Tsaymi Pascua aniversario galaycunanpagna caycaptin discïpuluncunawan cënananpag juntacargan. Tsaypäga Simonpa tsurin Judas Iscariotita Satanás maynami tantyatsishgana cargan autoridäcunaman Jesusta entregananpag. Discïpuluncunawan Jesús cënaycarmi mësapita sharcurcur janan cag röpanta jorgorgan. Nircurna discïpuluncunata cuyashganta tantyatsinanpag toällata tseglanman watacurcur paycunapa chaquincunata maylapargan. Maylaparcurnami toällawan chaquincunata sëcapargan. 
\p  
\v 6 Chaquinta maylapänanpag caycaptinmi Simón Pedro caynog nergan: “Tayta, chaquëta manami maylapämanquimantsu.” 
\p  
\v 7 Tsauraga Jesús caynog nergan: “Gam manami tantyanquitsu imanir maylapänäpag cashgantapis. Nircurragmi tantyanquipag.” 
\p  
\v 8 Tsauraga Pedro nergan: “Imanog captinpis chaquëta manami maylapämanquimantsu, tayta.” 
\p Tsaynog niptinmi Jesús nergan: “Chaquiquita mana maylapaptëga manami discïpulö canquimantsu.” 
\p  
\v 9 Niptinmi nergan: “Tsaynog captenga maquëtapis y umätapis maylapaycalämay, tayta.” 
\p  
\v 10 Tsauraga Jesús nergan: “Tsayrag armacushcunapaga chaquilanmi maylaypag caycan. Tsayrag armacushcuna limpio cashgannogmi jutsa rurashgayquipita perdonashgana car limpiuna carcaycanqui. Jucniquimi itsanga jutsancunata mana cachariptin armacöninog caycan.” 
\p  
\v 11 Tsaynog nergan juc discïpulun payta entregananpag cashganta musyarmi. 
\p  
\v 12 Discïpuluncunapa chaquinta maylapayta usharcurnami jorgushgan röpanta jaticurcur mësaman yapay jamacorgan. Nircurnami caynog nergan: “¿Tantyapäcunquicu imanir chaquiquicunata maylapashgätapis?  
\v 13-14 Yachatsicog caycar chaquiquicunata maylapaycaptëga gamcunapis ricacamashgayquinogla chaquiquicunata jucniqui jucniquipis maylapänacäriy.  
\v 15 Ashmaynogla tsaynog rurashcä ricacamar gamcunapis ashmaynogla canayquipagmi.\f + \fr 13:15 \ft Tsay witsanga ashmaycunalami jucpa chaquinta maylapag. Mana ashmay cagcunaga manami pipa chaquintapis maylapagtsu.\f* 
\v 16 Musyashgantsinogpis ashmayga manami patronninpita más munayniyogtsu caycan. Tsaynoglami cacha aywagpis cachagninpita más munayniyogtsu caycan.  
\v 17 Tsaynog captenga yätsishgänogla yanapanacorga cushishgami cawapäcunquipag. 
\s1 Juc discïpulun contran sharcunanpag cashganta Jesucristo wilashgan 
\r (Mateo 26.20-25; Marcos 14.17-21; Lucas 22.21-23) 
\p  
\v 18 “Manami lapayquipagtsu tsaynog niycä. Noga musyämi mayganiqui entregamänayquipag cashganta. Tayta Diospa palabranchöpis tsaynog cananpagmi caynog escribiraycan: ‘Nogawan micog cagmi conträ sharcushga.’\x + \xo 13:18 \xt Salmo 41.9\x* Tsay escribiraycashganga cumplengami.  
\v 19 Tsay escribiraycashgannog manarag pasaptinmi gamcunata wilapaycä tsaynog cananpag cashganta. Tsaymi nishgänogla pasaptin musyapäcunquipag Tayta Dios cachamashgan Cristo cashgäta.  
\v 20 Cachashgäcunata chasquicogcunaga nogatami chasquicaycäman. Tsaymi nogata chasquicamag cäga Taytätapis chasquicuycan.” 
\p  
\v 21 Tsaynog nircurmi Jesús pasaypa laquicushpan caynog nergan: “Gamcunapitami jucniqui conträcunapa maquinman entregamanquipag.” 
\p  
\v 22 Jesús tsaynog niptinmi discïpuluncuna jucnin jucninpis ricapänacorgan mayganpag niycashgantapis mana musyashpan.  
\v 23 Tsaychömi Jesuspa cuyay discïpulun paypa naupancho weguraycargan.  
\v 24 Paytami Simón Pedro sëñata gorgan mayganpag parlaycashgantapis Jesusta tapunanpag.  
\v 25 Tsaymi caynog taporgan: “¿Maygantag entregashogniqui caycan, tayta?” 
\p  
\v 26 Tsaynog tapuptinmi payta Jesús nergan: “Tsayga caycan tantata ushmarcatsir macyashgä cagmi.” 
\p Tsaynog nirmi tantata ushmarcatsir aptapargan Simonpa tsurin Judas Iscariotita.  
\v 27 Tsay tantata chasquircuptinmi payman Satanás yaycorgan. Nircurnami Jesús caynog nergan: “Ruranayquipag cagtaga jucla ruray.” 
\p  
\v 28 Tsaynog niptinpis manami discïpuluncuna tantyargantsu imanir tsaynog niycashgantapis.  
\v 29 Gastuncunapag guellayta puritseg captinmi waquincuna yarpapäcorgan cënaypag rantipacamog Jesús cachaycashganta. Waquin discïpuluncunami yarpapäcorgan wactsacunata yanapananpag cachaycashganta. 
\p  
\v 30 Tantata chasquircurnami Judas jucla aywargan yarpashgannog rurananpag. Tsayga cargan patsa tsacaycaptinnami. 
\s1 Cuyanacunanpag Jesucristo yachatsishgan 
\p  
\v 31-32 Judas yarguptinnami Jesús discïpuluncunata caynog nergan: “Hörä chaycämunnami \nd noga\nd* wanunäpag y nircur cawarimunäpagpis. Tsaynogpami runacuna tantyapäconga noga pï cashgäta y Tayta Dios munayniyog cashgantapis. 
\p  
\v 33 “Cuyay wamränog cagcuna, gamcunapita aywacunäpagnami caycä. Autoridänintsicunata nishgänoglami gamcunatapis caynog niycä: Nogata ashimarpis manami tarimanquipagtsu. Gamcunaga aywashgä cagman manaragmi chayanquipagragtsu. 
\p  
\v 34 “Aywacuptëpis jucniqui jucniqui cuyanacärinqui noga gamcunata cuyashgänogla. Tsay nishgäga mushog mandamientumi gamcunapag caycan.  
\v 35 Nishgänogla cuyanacäriptiquimi pï-maypis tantyapäconga discïpulöcuna cashgayquita.” 
\s1 Pedro ñëgananpag cagta Jesucristo nishgan 
\r (Mateo 26.31-35; Marcos 14.27-31; Lucas 22.31-34) 
\p  
\v 36 Tsauraga Simón Pedro taporgan: “¿Maypatag aywacunquipag, tayta?” 
\p Tsaynog tapuptin Jesús caynog nergan: “Noga aywashgä cagmanga manaragmi aywanquipagragtsu. Nircurnami itsanga aywanquipag.” 
\p  
\v 37 Tsaynami Pedro taporgan: “¿Imanirtag gamwan mana aywämantsu, tayta? Gam-raycu wanunäpagpis nogaga listumi caycä.” 
\p  
\v 38 Tsauraga Jesús nergan: “¿Rasunpacu noga-raycu wanunayquipag listu caycanqui? Tsaynog nirpis gällu manarag cantaptinmi reguimashgayquitapis quimsa cuti ñëgamanquipag.” 
\c 14  
\s1 Tayta Diosman chayanantsipag Jesucristo näni cashgan 
\p  
\v 1 “Ama laquicäriytsu. Tsaypa trucanga Tayta Diosman yäracäriy. Tsaynogla nogamanpis yäracamay.  
\v 2 Taytä cashgan cagchöga atscami wayicuna caycan tänayquipag. Tsaymanmi aywashag camarimunäpag. Tsay wayicuna mana captenga manami: ‘Camaricog aywashag’ nëmantsu.  
\v 3 Camarircamurnami cutimushag gamcunata pushanäpag. Tsaynogpami noga tashgä cagcho gamcunapis tanquipag.  
\v 4 Gamcuna musyanquimi mayman aywanäpag cashgantapis. Tsaynogpis musyanquimi maygan nänipa tsayman chayanayquipag cashgantapis.” 
\p  
\v 5 Tsauraga Tomás caynog nergan: “Mayman aywanayquipag cashgantapis mana musyaycarga ¿imanogpatag musyapäcöman maygan nänipa aywanäpag cashgantapis, tayta?” 
\p  
\v 6 Tsauraga Jesús nergan: “Nogami nänega caycä. Tsaynogpis nogapa wilacuynëga rasun cagmi caycan. Nogami runacunapag ali cawayta apamushcä. Tsaymi nogata mana chasquicamarga Taytä cashgan cagman mana pipis chayangapagtsu.  
\v 7 Nogata reguimag cäga Taytätapis reguinmi. Tsaymi cananpitaga musyapäcunquina Taytä imanog cashgantapis.” 
\p  
\v 8 Tsauraga Felipe nergan: “Nogaga manaragmi reguëragtsu. Tayta Diosta reguiycatsilämay nogapis reguinäpag.” 
\p  
\v 9 Tsauraga Jesús nergan: “Naupapitana gamcunawan caycaptëga ¿manacu cananyag reguimanquirag? Reguimag cäga Tayta Diostapis reguinmi. Reguiycämarga ¿imanirtag manacamanqui Tayta Diosta reguitsinäpag?  
\v 10 ¿Manacu criyinqui Tayta Dios nogawan caycashganta y nogapis paywan caycashgäta? Tsaymi imatapis parlarga pay munashgannogla parlaycä.  
\v 11 Tayta Dioswan noga caycashgäta y paypis nogawan caycashganta niycaptëga criyipäcamay. Nishgäcunata mana criyirpis milagro rurashgäcunata ricaycarga tantyacäriy rasun cagta niycashgäta. 
\p  
\v 12 “Wanushgäpita cawarircamur Taytä cagman cuticuptëmi chasquicamagcunaga noga rurashgänog milagruta rurangapag. Tsaynog milagruta ruraptinmi más atsca runacuna tantyacur nogata chasquicamanga.  
\v 13 Nogapa jutëcho Taytäta manacuptiquega manacushgayquita rurashagmi. Tsaynog rurashag may-tsaychöpis Tayta Dios alabashga cananpagmi.  
\v 14 Nogapa jutëcho manacuptiquega imatapis rurashagmi. 
\s1 Santu Espirituta cachamunanpag cashgan 
\p  
\v 15 “Nogata cuyamarga lapan nishgäcunata cäsucäriy.  
\v 16 Tayta Diostami manacushag Santu Espirituta gamcunaman cachamunanpag. Paynami imayyagpis gamcunawan caycanga yanapashunayquipag.  
\v 17 Tayta Diosta mana cäsucogcunaga Santu Espirituta manami chasquicärengatsu. Paycunaga manami tantyapäcuntsu Santu Espíritu cashgantapis. Gamcunami itsanga nogawan purir tantyanqui Santu Espíritu cashganta. Santu Espíritu shamurnami gamcunawan imayyagpis cangapag. 
\p  
\v 18-19 “Ama yarpapäcuytsu manana tincunantsipag cashgantaga, sinöga wanushgäpita cawarircamuptë yapaymi tincushunpag. Tayta Diosta mana cäsucogcunawanga manami tincushagnatsu. Noga wanurpis cawarimushgänoglami gamcunapis cawarimunquipag.  
\v 20 Tsay hörami tantyapäcunquipag Tayta Dioswan caycashgäta y gamcunawan caycashgätapis. 
\p  
\v 21 “Nishgäcunata cäsucog cäga rasunpami cuyaman. Paytaga Taytäpis y nogapis cuyashagmi. Tsaynogpis tantyatsishagmi imaypis paywan caycashgäta.” 
\p  
\v 22 Tsaynog niptinmi Santiagupa tsurin cag Judas caynog taporgan: “Nogacunawan canayquipag caycaptenga ¿imanirtag waquin runacunawanpis mana canquipagtsu?” 
\p  
\v 23 Tsauraga Jesús nergan: “Pipis cuyamarga nishgäcunata cäsucunmi. Cuyamar cäsucamagcunatami Taytäwan noga cuyashag. Tsaymi cawarircamur paycunawan imayyagpis cashag. Tsaynoglami Taytäpis paycunawan cangapag.  
\v 24 Nogata mana cuyamag cäga manami nishgäcunata cäsucuntsu. Y noga nishgäcunaga manami quiquëpa yarpayniläpitatsu caycan, sinöga cachamagnë Taytäpitami. 
\p  
\v 25 “Lapan caycunata niycä gamcunawan caycashgäyagmi.  
\v 26 Aywacuptënami Tayta Dios nogapa trucä gamcunaman Santu Espirituta cachamonga. Paymi lapan yachatsishgäcunata yarpätsishunquipag y tantyatsishunquipagpis. 
\p  
\v 27 “Gamcunapita aywacuptë ama laquicäriytsu ni mantsacäriytsu. Aywacurpis yanapaycäshayquimi ima pasashuptiquipis tranquïlo cawanayquipag. Noga yanapashgänöga manami pipis yanapashunquipagtsu.  
\v 28 Gamcunata nishcänami aywacurpis cutimunäpag cashganta. Lapanpagpis munayniyog Taytä cagman aywacuptë ama laquicunquitsu. Rasunpa cuyamarga laquicunayquipa trucanga cushicäriy.  
\v 29 Gamcunata tsaynog wilapaycä manarag aywacurmi. Aywacuptënami musyapäcunquipag nishgäcuna rasunpa cashganta. 
\p  
\v 30 “Satanás yarpätsishganta rurar prësu tsarimänanpag cag runacuna shamonganami. Tsaymi gamcunawan parlanäpag tiempo mana canganatsu. Satanasga imata ruramänanpagpis manami munayniyogtsu caycan.  
\v 31 Tsaynog caycaptinpis Taytäta cuyar cäsucushgäta lapan runacuna musyananpagmi pay nimashgannogla lapantapis cumplishag. Acu, caypita aywacushunna.” 
\c 15  
\s1 Üva yöraman Jesucristo tincutsicushgan 
\p  
\v 1 Tsaypitanami Jesús caynog nergan: “Nogaga caycä üva yöranogmi. Taytänami caycan üva uryagnog.  
\v 2 Nogaman yäracamagcuna üvapa rämancunanogmi caycan. Tsaymi maygan rämapis mana wayuptenga Taytä muturiycun. Wayog cagtami itsanga Taytä shumag rämapan más wayunanpag.  
\v 3 Üvata rämapaptin limpio cashgannogmi gamcunapis nishgäcunata chasquicur jutsayquicunapita limpiuna carcaycanqui. 
\p  
\v 4 “Ima rämapis yörancho mana carga manami wayuntsu. Tsaynoglami gamcunapis nogaman mana yäracamaptiquega Tayta Diosnintsi mana yanapashunquipagtsu pay munashgannog cawanayquipag. Tsaynog caycaptenga nogaman yäracamashpayqui imaypis cawapäcuy. Tsaynog yäracamaptiquega gamcunawanmi imaypis caycäshagpag. 
\p  
\v 5 “Noga caycä üva yöranogmi. Gamcunanami rämäcunanog carcaycanqui. Tsaymi cäsucamarga üva ali wayushgannog gamcunapis alita rurar cawapäcunquipag. Mana cäsucamarga manami imanogpapis Tayta Dios munashgannog cawanquipagtsu.  
\v 6 Pipis mana cäsucamag cäga yöranpita mutushga rämanogmi canga. Tsaynogpis tsay mutushga rämata shuntarcur rupatsishga cashgannogmi rupatsishga cangapag. 
\p  
\v 7 “Nogapa munaynëcho cawashpayqui yachatsishgäcunata imaypis cumpliptiquega Tayta Diosnintsi imata manacushgayquitapis mayashunquipagmi.  
\v 8 Noga munashgänog cawashpayquimi rasunpa discïpulöcuna carcaycanqui. Tsaynog cawaptiquimi runacuna tantyacushpan Tayta Diosta chasquicongapag. 
\p  
\v 9 “Taytä cuyamashgannogmi nogapis gamcunata cuyä. Tsaynog cuyaycaptëga imaypis cäsucamar cawapäcuy.  
\v 10 Nishgäcunata cäsucamaptiquega imaypis cuyashayquimi. Tsaynoglami nimashgancunata cäsucuptë nogatapis Taytä cuyaman.  
\v 11 Gamcunata tsaynog niycä noga cushishga cawashgänog gamcunapis cushishga cawapäcunayquipagmi. 
\p  
\v 12 “Nishgäcunata cäsucamashpayquega jucniqui jucniquipis cuyanacäriy gamcunata noga cuyashgänog.  
\v 13 Cuyashgantsi runataga ima pasaptinpis wanuy cawaymi yanapantsi.  
\v 14 Lapan nishgäcunata cäsucamaptiquega gamcunatapis wanuy cawaymi yanapashayqui.  
\v 15 Ashmaytaga manami patronnin wilapantsu imata yarpashgantapis. Gamcunata cuyarmi Taytä nimashgancunata lapanta wilapashcä. 
\p  
\v 16 “Manami acramashgayquipitatsu cuyä, sinöga gamcunata noga acrashgäpitami. Tsaymi gamcunata cachaycä Tayta Diosnintsipa wilacuyninta wilacuptiqui runacuna salvacionta tarinanpag. Wilacuptiqui yanapashunayquipäga nogapa jutëcho Taytäta manacärinqui. Manacuptiquega yanapashunquipagmi.  
\v 17 Tsaynog caycaptenga jucniqui jucniquipis cuyanacur cawapäcuy. 
\s1 Jesucristuta y payman yäracogcunata runacuna chiquishgan 
\p  
\v 18 “Runacuna chiquishuptiquega ama laquicäriytsu. Nogata chiquimashgannoglami gamcunatapis chiquishunquipag.  
\v 19 Paycunanog jutsata rurar cawaptiquimi itsanga cuyashunquiman. Chiquishuptiquipis Tayta Dios munashgannog cawanayquipagmi gamcunata acrashcä. 
\p  
\v 20 “ ‘Ashmayga manami patronninpita más munayniyogtsu’ nishgänoglami cananpis gamcunata caynog në: Patronta chiqueg cäga ashmaynincunatapis chiquinmi. Tsaynoglami nogata chiquimag cäga gamcunatapis chiquishunquipag, y nogata chasquicamag cäga gamcunatapis chasquishunquipagmi.  
\v 21 Runacuna chiquishunquipag discïpulöcuna cashgayquipitami. Paycunaga cachamagnë Taytä nishgancunata manami cäsucärintsu. 
\p  
\v 22-24 “Tayta Diosnintsipa wilacuyninta wilacur y pipis mana rurashgan milagrucunata rurarmi runacunata tantyatsishcä pay cachamashganta. Tsaynog tantyaycätsiptëpis runacunaga chiquimarmi jutsayog caycan. Mayganpis nogata chiquimag cäga Taytätapis chiquiycanmi.  
\v 25 Tayta Diosnintsipa palabranchöpis caynogmi niycan: ‘Jutsaynag caycaptëpis runacuna chiquimashgami.’\x + \xo 15:25 \xt Salmo 35.19; 69.4\x* Tsay escribirashgannoglami lapanpis cumpliycan. 
\p  
\v 26 “Gamcunamanmi Taytä cagpita Santu Espirituta cachamushag imaypis yanapashunayquipag. Tsaynogpis paymi nogapita tantyatsishunqui.  
\v 27 Gamcunapis nogawan imaypis purishga caycarga nogapita runacunata tantyatsipäcuy. 
\c 16  
\p  
\v 1 “Tsay lapanta gamcunata niycä runacuna chiquishuptiquipis nogaman imaypis yäracamänayquipagmi.  
\v 2 Chiquishushpayquimi sinagogapitapis gargushunquipag. Tsaynogpis Tayta Dios munashganta ruraycashganta yarparmi wanutsishunquipag.  
\v 3 Tsaynog rurapäcushunquipag nogata ni Taytätapis mana chasquicamarmi.  
\v 4 Tsaynog pasashuptiqui yarpapäcuy nishgänogla lapanpis cumpliycashganta. Naupataga gamcunata manami wilargäragtsu tsaynog pasashunayquipag cashganta. Aywacunäpag carnami chiquishga canayquipag cashganta wilaycä. 
\s1 Santu Espíritu shamunanpag cashgan 
\p  
\v 5-6 “Cananga Taytä cagman cuticunäpagnami caycä. Tsaynog captinpis: ‘¿Maypatag aywanqui?’ nir tapumänayquipa trucanga ¿imanirtag laquishga carcaycanqui?  
\v 7 Ama laquicäriytsu. Aywacurpis Santu Espiritutami cachamushag gamcunawan cananpag. Mana aywacuptëga manami Santu Espíritu shamongatsu.  
\v 8 Pay shamurnami runacunata tantyatsenga jutsayog cashganta, Tayta Diosta mana cäsucog cashganta y jutsata rurashganpita juzgashga cananpag cashgantapis.  
\v 9 Jutsayog cashgantaga Santu Espíritu tantyatsenga nogata mana chasquicamaptinmi.  
\v 10 Tayta Diosta mana cäsucog cashgantaga Santu Espíritu tantyatsenga Taytä cagman cuticuptëmi.\f + \fr 16:10 \ft Jesucristo cay patsacho car runacunata tantyatsergan paycuna Tayta Diosta mana cäsucushganta. Ciëluman cuticuptinnami Santu Espirituna runacunata tantyaycätsin mana cäsucushganta.\f* 
\v 11 Runacunata Tayta Dios juzgananpag cashganta Santu Espíritu tantyatsenga Satanás vincishgana captinmi. 
\p  
\v 12 “Atscaragmi caycan gamcunata yachatsinäpag. Tsaynog captinpis manami lapantaga yachatsishayquiragtsu. Lapanta yachatsiptëga manami yarpanquipagtsu.  
\v 13 Santu Espíritu shamurnami mana yachatsishgä cagcunata tantyatsishunquipag. Tsaynoglami tantyatsishunquipag ima pasananpag cagcunatapis.  
\v 14 Santu Espíritu nogapita tsaynog tantyatsishunquipag noga alabashga canäta munarmi.  
\v 15 Taytäpa maquincho cagcunaga nogapa maquëchömi carcaycan. Tsaynog captinmi nishcä Santu Espíritu nogapita tantyatsishunayquipag cashganta. 
\s1 Laquicushganpita discïpuluncuna cushicunanpag cashgan 
\p  
\v 16 “Más rätutaga nogata manami ricapäcamanquipagnatsu. Tsaypita warantincunaga yapaymi gamcuna ricamanquipag.” 
\p  
\v 17 Tsaynog niptin discïpuluncuna jucninpis jucninpis caynog nipäcorgan: “Tsaynog nishpan ¿imatarag niycämantsi? ¿Imanirrag nimantsi: ‘Más rätutaga manami ricamanquipagnatsu’? Y nircorga ¿imanirrag niycan: ‘Tsaypita warantincunaga yapaymi ricamanquipag’? Tsaynogpis ¿imanirrag: ‘Taytä cagman aywacushagmi’ niycämantsi?  
\v 18 ¿Imaypitarag payta mana ricashuntsu? Manami tantyantsitsu imata parlaycashgantapis.” 
\p  
\v 19 Discïpuluncuna tsaynog yarpachacärishganta musyarmi Jesús caynog nergan: “¿‘Más rätutaga manami ricapäcamanquipagnatsu’ y ‘Tsaypita warantincunaga yapaymi ricapäcamanquipag’ nishgäpitacu gamcuna yarpachacurcaycanqui?  
\v 20 Aywacuptë waquincuna cushicuptinpis gamcunaga laquicushpayqui wagapäcunquipagmi. Tsaynog laquicurpis nircorga cushicärinquipagmi.  
\v 21 Musyantsimi wachay nanay tsariptin warmicuna laquicärishganta. Yuripacurirnami itsanga cushicur manana yarpannatsu nanaywan nacashgantapis.  
\v 22 Tsaynoglami gamcuna canan laquicurpis yapay tincuptintsi cushicärinquipag. Tsay cushicushgayquitaga ima pasashuptiquipis manami gonganquipagtsu.  
\v 23 Yapay tincuptintsega mananami tapupäcamanquipagnatsu imanir tsaynog parlashgätapis. 
\p “Shumag tantyacäriy. Nogapa jutëcho manacuptiquega Taytä mayashunquipagmi.  
\v 24 Naupataga Taytäta manacurpis manami jutëchötsu manacärishcanqui. Cananpitaga nogapa jutëcho Taytäta imatapis manacäriy. Manacuptiquega manacushgayquita mayashunquipagmi. Manacushgayquita mayaptinmi cushicärinquipag. 
\p  
\v 25 “Gamcunata cananyag imamanpis tincutsiypa yachatsiptë manami shumag tantyapäcamashcanquitsu. Nircurmi itsanga gamcunata yachatsishayqui imamanpis mana tincutsiylapana. Tsaynog yachatsiptëmi itsanga lapan nishgäcunatapis tantyapäcunquipag.  
\v 26 Yachatsishgäcunata tantyacurnami nogapa jutëchöna Tayta Diosta manacärinquipag. Tsaymi mana shuyarangatsu nogarag gamcunapag manacunäta, sinöga gamcuna manacushgayquitapis mayashunquipagmi.  
\v 27 Tayta Diosnintsega gamcunata cuyashunquimi. Tsaynog cuyashunqui paypita shamushgäta criyir cuyapäcamaptiquimi.  
\v 28 Taytäpa naupanpitami cay patsaman noga shamushcä. Tsaynoglami Taytäpa naupanman cuticushagpag.” 
\p  
\v 29 Tsauraga discïpuluncuna caynog nergan: “¡Cananmi itsanga nimashgayquicunata tantyapäcö! Mananami tumatsipaylapanatsu parlapaycämanqui.  
\v 30 Tsaynogpami musyapäcö gam lapanta musyashgayquita. Tantyatsimänayquipag mana manacuptëpis tantyatsipäcamanquimi. Tsaymi Tayta Diospa naupanpita shamushgayquita criyipäcö.” 
\p  
\v 31 Tsauraga Jesús caynog nergan: “¿Rasunpacu criyircaycämanqui?  
\v 32 Cananga höra chämushganami japaläta cachariycamar wacpa caypa aywacärinayquipag. Tsaynog cacharimaptiquipis manami japalätsu caycäshag, sinöga Taytäwanmi cashagpag. 
\p  
\v 33 “Gamcunata tsaynog niycä runacuna chiquishuptiquipis mana ajayaypa imaypis yäracamänayquipagmi. Cay patsacho cashgayquiyäga nacapäcunquiragmi. Nogapis nacar gamcuna-raycu wanurmi Satanasta vincishagpag. Tsaynog captenga cay patsacho nacarpis ama laquicäriytsu.” 
\c 17  
\s1 Tayta Diosta Jesucristo manacushgan 
\p  
\v 1 Tsaypitanami jana patsata ricärir Tayta Diosta Jesús manacorgan caynog nir: “Wanunäpag cag hörä chayaycämunnami, papá. Wanuptëpis cawariycatsilämay munayniyog cashgayquita runacuna tantyapäcunanpag.  
\v 2 Gammi lapan runapagpis munayniyog canäpag churamashcanqui. Tsaynogpis churamashcanqui acrashgayqui cagcunata perdonar salvanäpagmi.  
\v 3 Salvashgana car gloriaman chayarmi reguishushpayqui gam japalayqui Dios cashgayquita musyangapag, papá. Tsaynoglami naupayquicho caycagta ricamashpan cay patsaman cachamashgayquitapis musyangapag. 
\p  
\v 4 “Lapan shongöwanmi nimashgayquicunata cay patsacho cumplishcä.  
\v 5 Cay patsata manarag camar naupayquicho munayniyog cashgänog cananpis munayniyog canäpag pushacalämayna, papá. 
\p  
\v 6 “Tsaynoglami discïpulöcunapagpis gamta manacamö, papá. Paycunataga acrashcanqui maquëcho cawapäcunanpagmi. Tsaymi paycunaga wilacuyniquita yachatsiptë chasquicärishga.  
\v 7-8 Tsaynog chasquicurmi cananga musyapäcunna lapan yachatsishgäcuna gam munashgayquinogla cashganta. Tsaynogpis yachatsishgäta chasquicurmi tantyapäcushga gam cachamashgayquita.  
\v 9 Discïpulöcunapag manacamur manami lapan runacunapagtsu manacamö, sinöga maquëman churamushgayqui cagcunalapagmi.  
\v 10 Nogapa maquëcho carga gampa maquiquichöpis caycanmi, papá. Paycunaga tantyacärishgami gam cachamashgayquita. 
\p  
\v 11 “Nogaga gampa naupayquimanna shacamur manami cay patsacho cashagpagnatsu. Paycunami itsanga cay patsacho caycangarag. Tsaymi paycunapag gamta manacamö imaypis yachatsishgänogla cawapäcunanpag. Tsaynogpami nogantsi tsay yarpayla cashgantsinog paycunapis cuyanacur tsay yarpayla cangapag.  
\v 12 Cay patsacho cashpä maquëman churamushgayqui cagcunataga lapantami shumag ricashcä. Tsaynog ricaptëmi mayganpis nogaman yäracamashganpita mana witicushgatsu. Jucmi itsanga Satanás munashganta rurar witicushga. Pay witicunanpäga palabrayquicho maynami escribiraycashga. 
\p  
\v 13 “Gampa naupayquiman cutimunäpag captinmi cushishga caycä, papá. Tsaymi discïpulöcunapag gamta manacamö noga cushishga cashgänog paycunapis cushishga cawapäcunanpag.  
\v 14 Gampa wilacuyniquita paycunata maynami wilapashcä. Tsayta cäsucur manami waquin runacunanognatsu cawarcaycan, sinöga noga cawashgänognami cawarcaycan. Tsaynog cawaptinmi runacuna paycunata chiquipäcun.  
\v 15 Runacuna chiquiptinpis manami cay patsapita jucla pushacunayquipagtsu gamta manacamö, sinöga cay patsacho cashganyag Satanaspita tsapaycunayquipagmi.  
\v 16 Imanog captinpis naupayquicho cawanäpag cashgannogmi paycunapis naupayquicho cawananpag carcaycan. 
\p  
\v 17 “Wilacuyniquita wilapashgäta paycunata shumag yarpaycatsilay, papá. Wilacuyniquita yarpashpanmi gam munashgayquinog shumag cawapäcongapag.  
\v 18 Wilacunäpag cachamashgayquinoglami paycunatapis noga cachaycä ali wilacuyniquita wilacärinanpag.  
\v 19 Munashgayquinog paycuna cawananpagmi nogapis wilacuyniqui nishgannogla cawaycä. 
\p  
\v 20 “Manami paycunalapagtsu gamta manacamö, sinöga paycuna wilacushganta chasquicogcunapagpis manacamömi.  
\v 21 Nogantsi juc yarpayla cashgantsinog paycunapis juc yarpayla cananpagmi gamta manacamö, papá. Tsaynog cawashganta ricacurmi cachamashgayquita tantyar waquin runacunapis chasquicamangapag.  
\v 22 Nogantsi cuyanacur cawashgantsinog paycunapis cuyanacur cawapäcunanpagmi wilacuyniquita yachatsishcä.  
\v 23 Cuyanacur cawapäcunanpagmi paycunawan imaypis caycäshag. Tsaynoglami gampis nogawan caycanqui. Cuyanacur cawapäcushganta ricarmi cachamashgayquita tantyashpan waquin runacunapis chasquicamangapag. Tsaynogpis tantyapäconga nogata cuyamashgayquinog paycunatapis cuyashgayquita. 
\p  
\v 24 “Lapan acrashgayqui cagcuna gloriacho nogawan canantami munä. Gloriacho carnami ricapäcamanga pasaypa chip-chipyaycar munayniyog cashgäta. Tsaynogmi cargä cay patsata manarag camaptintsipis. Tsaynog munayniyog caycagta ricamänantami munä, papá. 
\p  
\v 25-26 “Gam imata munashgayquitapis runacuna manami tantyantsu. Nogami itsanga tantyä, gampa naupayquipita shamushga car. Chasquicamagcunapis munashgayquita tantyananpagmi paycunata yachatsishcä. Wanushgäpita cawarircamur mastapis munashgayquita yachatsishagragmi. Tsaynogpami cuyanacushgantsinog paycunapis cuyanacur cawangapag. Tsaycunatami gamta manacamö, papá.” 
\c 18  
\s1 Jesucristuta prësu tsaripäcushgan 
\r (Mateo 26.47-56; Marcos 14.43-50; Lucas 22.47-53) 
\p  
\v 1 Tayta Diosta Jesús manacuyta usharcurmi discïpuluncunawan tsimpapäcorgan Cedrón nishgan ragrata. Tsimparirnami chayapäcorgan Olivos yöracuna cashgan chacraman. 
\p  
\v 2 Discïpuluncunawan Jesús cadala tsayman aywashga captinmi Jesusta entregag cag Judas Iscariote musyargan tsayman aywapäcushganta.  
\v 3 Tsaymi Jesuspa contran cag runacunata pushacurcur Judas tsayman aywargan Jesusta entregananpag. Tsay runacunaga cargan mandag cüracuna y fariseo runacuna cachashgan wardiacuna y atsca soldäducunami. Paycunami aywapäcorgan atsquincunawan y espädancunawanpis. 
\p  
\v 4 Prësu tsarinanpag shamushganta musyaycarpis Jesús aywargan tsay runacunawan tincunanpag. Tincurmi caynog taporgan: “¿Pitatag gamcuna ashircaycanqui?” 
\p  
\v 5 Tsauraga caynog nipäcorgan: “Nazaret marcapita cag Jesustami ashircaycä.” 
\p Tsaymi Jesús nergan: “Nogami caycä.” 
\p  
\v 6 Jesús: “Nogami caycä” niptinmi lapan runacuna mantsarishpan ancalaypa tunicärergan. Judas Iscariotipis paycunawanmi caycargan.  
\v 7 Tsauraga Jesús yapay taporgan: “¿Pitatag ashircaycanqui?” 
\p Niptinmi yapay nipäcorgan: “Nazaret marcapita cag Jesustami ashircaycä.” 
\p  
\v 8 Tsauraga Jesús nergan: “Maynami nishcä noga cashgäta. Nogata ashimarga nogalata prësu apapäcamay. Discïpulöcunataga ama tsaripäcuytsu.” 
\p  
\v 9 Tsaynog pasananpagmi discïpuluncunapag mayna caynog nergan: “Discïpulöcunataga shumagmi ricashcä nogaman yäracamashganpita mayganpis mana witicärinanpag.”\x + \xo 18:9 \xt San Juan 6.38,39\x* 
\p  
\v 10 Tsauraga Simón Pedro espädanta jorgurir juc runapa derëcha cag rinrinta roguriycorgan. Tsay runa cargan más mandag cürapa ashmayninmi. Paypa jutinmi cargan Malco.  
\v 11 Tsaynog ruraptinmi Pedruta Jesús nergan: “¡Espädayquita cutitsiy churaräcunanman! Wanunäta Taytä munaptenga listumi caycä wanunäpagpis.” 
\s1 Más mandag cüraman Jesucristuta apapäcushgan 
\r (Mateo 26.57-58; Marcos 14.53-54; Lucas 22.54) 
\p  
\v 12 Nircurnami Jesusta liyacurcur lapan soldäducuna mandagninwan y wardiacunapis payta apapäcorgan.  
\v 13 Nircurnami chayatsipäcorgan Anaspa wayinman. Anasga cargan Caifaspa suedrunmi. Caifasga cargan más mandag cürami.  
\v 14 Autoridä mayincunata Caifasga maynami caynog nergan: “Tsay runala wanutsun lapantsi salvacunantsipag.”\x + \xo 18:14 \xt San Juan 11.49-52\x* 
\s1 Jesucristuta Pedro ñëgashgan 
\r (Mateo 26.69-70; Marcos 14.66-68; Lucas 22.55-57) 
\p  
\v 15 Simón Pedruwan jucag discïpulunmi Jesusta gatirargan caru guepalanta. Jucag discïpulunmi más mandag cürawan reguinacushga car sawan rurinman yaycorgan Jesuspa guepanta.  
\v 16 Pedroga quëdacuycorgan punculachömi. Tsaymi puncucho cuidag warmita más mandag cürawan reguinacog discïpuloga ruwacorgan Pedrutapis ruriman yaycatsinanpag. 
\p  
\v 17 Tsaymi puncucho cuidag warmi Pedruta caynog taporgan: “¿Manacu gampis tsay runapa discïpulun caycanqui?” 
\p Tsauraga Pedro nergan: “Manami nogaga paypa discïpuluntsu cä.” 
\p  
\v 18 Tsauraga fiyupa gasaptinmi ninata ratarcatsir mashacurcaycargan ashmaycuna y templo täpag wardiacunapis. Tsaychömi Pedrupis paycunawan mashacuycargan. 
\s1 Más mandag cüra Jesucristuta tapushgan 
\r (Mateo 26.59-66; Marcos 14.55-64; Lucas 22.66-71) 
\p  
\v 19 Tsaypitanami Jesusta Anás taporgan discïpuluncuna pï cashganta y imata yachatsishgantapis.  
\v 20-21 Tsaymi Jesús caynog nergan: “¿Imanirtag tsaynog tapumanqui? Nogaga manami imatapis pacaylapaga yachatsishcätsu. Sinagogacunacho y templuchöpis yachatsiptë lapan runacunami mayamashga. Yachatsishgäta mayamag runacunata tapumuy. Paycunami musyan imata yachatsishgätapis.” 
\p  
\v 22 Tsaynog niptinmi juc wardia Jesusta lagyargan caynog nir: “¿Imanirtag más mandag cürata tsaynog ninqui?” 
\p  
\v 23 Tsaynog niptinmi Jesús nergan: “¿Imatatag mana alita parlashcä? Mana alita parlashga captëga mä tantyatsimay. Lutanta mana parlaycaptëga ¿imanirtag lagyamanqui?” 
\p  
\v 24 Nircurnami liyashgalata Jesusta Anás apatsergan más mandag cüra Caifás cagman. 
\s1 Jesucristuta Pedro yapay ñëgashgan 
\r (Mateo 26.71-75; Marcos 14.69-72; Lucas 22.58-62) 
\p  
\v 25 Tsayyagmi Simón Pedro mashacuycargan waquin runacuna mashacuycashgan cagcho. Tsaycho mashacuycaptinmi caynog nipäcorgan: “¿Gampis manacu tsay runapa discïpulun canqui?” 
\p Tsauraga Pedro nergan: “Nogaga manami paypa discïpuluntsu cä.” 
\p  
\v 26 Maylantanami más mandag cürapa ashmayninpis caynog nergan: “Gamta paywan caycagtami ricashcä olivos yöracuna cashgan chacracho.” 
\p (Tsaynog neg runapa castanpa rinrintami Pedro rogurergan.) 
\p  
\v 27 Tsauraga Pedro yapay caynog nergan: “Manami paypa discïpuluntsu cä.” Tsaynog niycaptinmi gällu cantarcorgan. 
\s1 Pilätuman Jesucristuta prësu apapäcushgan 
\r (Mateo 27.1-2, 11-14; Marcos 15.1-5; Lucas 23.1-5) 
\p  
\v 28 Patsa manarag waraptinmi Caifaspa wayinpita Jesusta apapäcorgan Pilätupa despächunman. Payga Roma autoridämi cargan. Israel autoridäcunami itsanga tsayman mana yaycapäcorgantsu caynog nishpan: “Roma runapa wayinman yaycorga leynintsi nishgannog Pascua aniversario micuycunata manami micushunpagnatsu.”  
\v 29 Tsaymi despächunpita yargurir Pilato taporgan caynog nir: “¿Ima jutsatatag cay runa rurashga cayman apamunayquipäga?” 
\p  
\v 30 Tsaynog tapuptinmi nipäcorgan: “Jutsayog captinmi cayman apapäcamushcä. Jutsan mana captenga manami apapäcamömantsu cargan.” 
\p  
\v 31 Tsauraga Pilato caynog nergan: “Noga juzganäta munarga wilapäcamay ima jutsan cashgantapis. Sinöga, payta apacäriy leyniquicuna escribirashgannog quiquiquicuna juzgapäcunayquipag.” 
\p Tsaynog niptinmi Israel runacunapa autoridänincuna nipäcorgan: “Musyashgayquinogpis nogacunaga manami munayniyogtsu carcaycä pitapis wanutsinäpag.” 
\p  
\v 32 Tsaynog nirmi Pilätuta manacärergan Jesusta cruzcho wanutsinanpag. Cruzcho wanutsiptinmi cumplergan Jesús crucificashga cananpag nishganta.\x + \xo 18:32 \xt San Juan 12.32-33\x* 
\p  
\v 33 Despächunman Pilato yaycurirmi Jesusta gayaycur taporgan caynog nir: “¿Rasunpacu gamga canqui Israel runacunapa mandagnin rey?” 
\p  
\v 34 Tsauraga Jesús caynog nergan: “¿Musyayta munarcu tsaynog tapumanqui, o Israel autoridäcuna nishuptiquicu tsaynog tapumanqui?” 
\p  
\v 35 Tsaynog niptin Pilato nergan: “Nogaga manami Israel runatsu cä tsaycunata musyaycänäpäga. Marca mayiquicunawan mandag cüracunami prësu apamushushcanqui. ¿Imatatag rurashcanqui prësu apamushunayquipag?” 
\p  
\v 36 Tsauraga Jesús nergan: “Nogaga manami cay patsacho mandagtsu cä. Cay patsacho mandag captëga nogaman yäracamagcuna pelyanmanmi cargan autoridäcuna prësu mana tsarimänanpag.” 
\p  
\v 37 Tsaynog niptin Pilato taporgan: “¿Tsaynog captenga rasunpacu Israel runacunapa mandagnin rey caycanqui?” 
\p Tsauraga Jesús nergan: “Au, gam nishgayquinoglami mandag rey caycä. Mandag rey canäpagmi cay patsacho yurishcä. Tsaynogpis cay patsaman shamushcä Tayta Diosnintsipa wilacuyninta wilacunäpagmi. Tayta Diosnintsipa wilacuyninta chasquicogcunaga nishgäcunata chasquicärinmi.” 
\p  
\v 38 Tsaynog niptin Pilato nergan: “¿Cantsuragpis manatsuragpis Diospa wilacuynenga?” 
\s1 Jesucristuta crucificananpag Pilato mandashgan 
\r (Mateo 27.15-31; Marcos 15.6-20; Lucas 23.13-25) 
\p Jesusta tapurcushpan despächunpita Pilato yapay yargurir Israel runacunapa autoridänincunata caynog nergan: “Noga manami tarëtsu cay runapa ima jutsantapis.  
\v 39 Gamcunaga musyapäcunquimi Pascua aniversariucho juc prësuta cacharinäpag cashganta. ¿Munapäcunquicu Israel runacunapa mandagnin rey Jesusta cacharinäta?” 
\p  
\v 40 Tsaynog niptin nipäcorgan: “¡Barrabasta cachariyga! ¡Jesustaga ama cachariytsu!” 
\p Barrabasga cargan Romacho mandag emperadorpa contranmi. 
\c 19  
\p  
\v 1 Mana cacharinanpag nipäcuptinmi Pilato astatsergan Jesusta.  
\v 2 Soldäducunami cashapita corönata rurarcur Jesuspa umanman jatipargan. Tsaynogpis puca-chicnu cäpata aylupargan.  
\v 3 Nircurnami Jesusta lagyashpan caynog nipäcorgan: “¡Alabashga catsun Israel runacunapa mandagnin rey!” 
\p  
\v 4 Despächunpita Pilato yapay yargurcur caynog nergan: “Yapaymi tsay runata jorgamushag jutsaynag cashganta tantyapäcunayquipag.” 
\p  
\v 5 Tsaynog nirmi Jesusta jorgamorgan cashapita rurashga corönan jatishgata y puca-chicnu cäpan jatishgata. Tsauraga Pilato nergan: “¡Ricapäcuy cay runata!” 
\p  
\v 6 Tsauraga Jesusta ricaycurmi Israel runacunapa autoridänincunawan templo täpag wardiacunapis nipäcorgan: “¡Crucificashga catsun! ¡Crucificashga catsun!” 
\p Tsaynog nipäcuptinmi Pilato nergan: “Crucificashga cananta munarga quiquiquicuna crucificay ima, ari.\f + \fr 19:6 \ft Israel runacunata munaynincho tsararar Roma runacuna manami munargantsu Israel runacuna jutsayogcunata wanutsinanta. Tsaypa trucanga quiquin Roma autoridäcunaragmi jutsayogcunata wanutsergan. Tsaymi Pilato: “Tsauraga gamcuna crucificapäcuy” niptinpis Israel autoridäcuna payta yapay manacärergan Jesusta crucificatsinanpag.\f* Nogaga manami ima jutsantapis paypata tarëtsu wanutsishga cananpäga.” 
\p  
\v 7 Tsaynog niptinmi tsay autoridäcuna nipäcorgan: “Cay runaga: ‘Diospa tsurinmi cä’ nishganpita wanutsishga catsun. Tsaynog negcuna wanutsishga cananpagmi leynëcunacho niycan.” 
\p  
\v 8 “Diospa tsurinmi cä” nishganta wilapäcuptinmi Pilato fiyupa mantsarergan.  
\v 9 Tsauraga despächunman cutiycur Jesusta yapay taporgan caynog nir: “¿Gam maypitatag caycanqui?” 
\p Tsaynog tapuptin Jesús manami imatapis rimacorgantsu.  
\v 10 Tsauraga Pilato nergan: “Tapuycaptëga ¿manacu imatapis contestamanqui? Crucificatsinäpag o cacharinäpagpis munayniyog cashgäta ¿gam manacu musyanqui?” 
\p  
\v 11 Tsaynog niptin Jesús nergan: “Gampa maquiquiman Tayta Dios mana churamaptenga manami ima munayniquipis canmantsu crucificatsimänayquipag ni cacharimänayquipagpis. Tsaymi gampita más jutsayog caycan maquiquiman entregamag cag runa.” 
\p  
\v 12 Tsaynog niptinmi Pilätoga cachariyta munargan. Cachariyta munaptinmi Israel runacunapa autoridänincuna masrag gaparpargan caynog nir: “¡Mandag-tucurmi Jesusga emperador Cesarpa contran caycan! ¡Tsaymi Jesusta cacharerga gampis emperador Cesarpa contran canquipag!” 
\p  
\v 13 Tsaynog nipäcuptinmi Pilato jorgatsimorgan Jesusta. Nircurnami “Gábata” nishgan alarman aywaycur mandacunan sillëtaman jamacorgan. (Hebreo idiömachöga Gábata nishganga “Läja rumicunawan rurashga” ninanmi.)  
\v 14 Tsaypitami Israel runacunapa autoridänincunata caynog nergan: “¡Mandagniqui reyta ricapäcuy!” 
\p (Tsaycuna pasargan viernes pulan junagmi. Tsay tardi sábado jamay junag galaycorgan.) 
\p  
\v 15 Tsauraga runacuna fuertipa caynog nipäcorgan: “¡Wanutsishga catsun! ¡Wanutsishga catsun! ¡Crucificatsiy!” 
\p Tsaymi Pilato nergan: “¿Mandagniquita crucificatsinätacu munapäcunqui?” 
\p Tsauraga cürapa mandagnincunami caynog nipäcorgan: “¡Nogacunapa mandagnëga emperador Cesarlami! ¡Paypita juc mandagnëga manami pipis cantsu!” 
\p  
\v 16 Tsaynog nipäcuptinmi Jesusta Pilato entregaycorgan crucificashga cananpag. 
\s1 Jesucristuta crucificashgan 
\r (Mateo 27.32-44; Marcos 15.21-32; Lucas 23.26-43) 
\p  
\v 17 Tsaymi Jesusta apapäcorgan cruzta umrurcatsir “Calavëra” nishgan jircaman. (Hebreo idiömachöga Gólgota nipäcun tsay jircata.)  
\v 18 Tsayman chayaycatsirnami Jesusta crucificargan. Tsaynogmi ishcay runacunatapis crucificapäcorgan Jesuspa ishcan naupanman. 
\p  
\v 19 Tsaypitanami Pilato clävatsergan cruzpa puntanman juc letrëruta. Tsay letrëruchömi caynog escribirargan: “Nazaretpita cag Jesús, Israel runacunapa mandagnin reymi.”  
\v 20 Jerusalenpa cercalancho crucificashga captinmi Israel runacuna atsca liyipäcorgan tsay letrërucho escribiraycagta. Tsay letrëroga escribirargan hebreo, latín y griego idiömacunachömi.  
\v 21 Tsaymi mandag cüracuna caynog nipäcorgan Pilätuta: “ ‘Israel runacunapa mandagnin reymi’ nerga ama escribirätsuntsu, sinöga: ‘Israel runacunapa mandagnin rey-tucogmi’ nishpan escribirätsonga.” 
\p  
\v 22 Tsaynog niptin Pilato nergan: “Escribishgäga escribishganami caycan.” 
\p  
\v 23 Jesusta crucificaycurnami paypa röpanta tsaycho cag chuscu soldäducuna aypunacärergan. Rurincho cag jatirashgan röpata aypunacunanpagmi itsanga, costüraynag captin, caynog nipäcorgan:  
\v 24 “Tsaytaga ama rachishuntsu, sinöga suertitarag jitashun maygantsipis apacunantsipag.” 
\p Tsaynogpami cumplergan Tayta Diospa palabrancho Jesuspag caynog escribirashgan: “Suertitami jitapäcushga mayganpis röpäta apacunanpag.”\x + \xo 19:24 \xt Salmo 22.18\x* Tsay nishgannoglami soldäducuna rurapäcorgan. 
\p  
\v 25 Crucificaraycashgan cagchömi caycargan Jesuspa maman, mamanpa nanan, Cleofaspa warmin María y María Magdalenapis.  
\v 26 Tsaymi mamanta y cuyashgan discïpulunta ricärishpan Jesús caynog nergan: “Mamä, nogapa trucä Juannami wawayqui canga.” 
\p  
\v 27 Nircurnami cuyashgan discïpuluntapis caynog nergan: “Cananga mamäta ricayculanqui mamayquitanog.” 
\p Jesús tsaynog niptinmi tsay junagpitana mamanta pushacorgan wayinman. 
\s1 Jesucristo wanushgan 
\r (Mateo 27.45-56; Marcos 15.33-41; Lucas 23.44-49) 
\p  
\v 28 Wanunanpag carnami Tayta Diosnintsipa palabrancho escribiraycashgan cumplinanpag Jesús caynog nergan: “Yacunaycämi.”\x + \xo 19:28 \xt Salmo 22.15; 69.21\x* 
\p  
\v 29 Tsaychömi soldäducuna upunanpag cag pochgog vïnu caycargan wichi junta. Tsaymi gueru puntanman hisöputa rurarcur tsay pochgog vïnuman ushmarcatsir Jesusta shogutsiyta munargan.  
\v 30 Tsay vïnuta yawarcurnami Jesús nergan: “Lapantanami cumplishcä.” 
\p Tsaynog nircushpannami wanorgan. 
\s1 Jesucristupa lapsha pachanpa soldädo tucsishgan 
\p  
\v 31 Pascua aniversariucho sábado jamay junag galaycunanpagna caycaptinmi\f + \fr 19:31 \ft Israel runacunapäga sábado jamay junag galaycorgan viernes las seis tardimi.\f* Israel runacunapa autoridänincuna mana munapäcorgantsu pipis crucificaraycar quëdananta. Tsaymi Pilätuta manacärergan cruzcho wanuyta nacaycagcunapa chancancunata paquircur cruzpita jorgunanpag.\f + \fr 19:31 \ft Crucificaraycagpa chancancunata avëcis paquipäcog rasla wanunanpagmi. Chancanta paquircuptinnami imamanpis ichicuyta mana camäpacushpan jämaytsaypa wanog.\f* 
\v 32 Tsaymi soldäducuna aywaycushpan Jesuspa naupancho crucificaraycag runacunapa chancancunata paquipäcorgan.  
\v 33 Jesuspa chancancunatami itsanga manana paquergannatsu, wanushgana caycagta tariycur. 
\p  
\v 34 Wanushgana caycaptinpis lapsha pachanpa Jesusta tucsergan juc soldädo. Tsaynog tucsiptinmi yargamorgan yawarwan yacu.  
\v 35 Jesuspa discïpulun carmi lapan tsaycunata ricargä. Tsaymi imanog cashgantapis escribiycä salvamagnintsi Cristo cashganta gamcunapis criyipäcunayquipag.  
\v 36 Lapan tsaycunaga pasargan: “Manami ni juc tululanpis paquishgatsu canga”\x + \xo 19:36 \xt Éxodo 12.46; Números 9.12; Salmo 34.20\x* nir Tayta Diosnintsipa palabrancho escribiraycashgan cumplinanpagmi.  
\v 37 “Runacuna ricapäcongami tucsishganta”\x + \xo 19:37 \xt Zacarías 12.10\x* nir escribiraycashganpis cumplerganmi. 
\s1 Jesucristuta pampapäcushgan 
\r (Mateo 27.57-61; Marcos 15.42-47; Lucas 23.50-56) 
\p  
\v 38 Tsaypitami Arimatea marcapita José jutiyog runa Pilätuta manacorgan caynog nir: “Jesuspa ayanta cachapaycalämay pampag apanäpag.” Israel autoridäcunata mantsacushpanmi payga Jesusman yäracushganta mana wilacorgantsu. Manacushganta Pilato auniptinmi Jesuspa ayanta apargan pampananpag.  
\v 39 Tsaynogmi Nicodemupis paywan aywargan quimsa arröba mïrra y aloe nishganta\f + \fr 19:39 \ft Mïrraga cargan yörapa weguinmi. Aloipis cargan juc yörami. Tsaycunatami Israel runacuna tsaquircatsir ñutgu agapäcog. Nircurmi ayaman winapäcog mana asyänanpag.\f* apacurcur.  
\v 40 Israel runacunapa costumbrin cashgannogmi tsay apashganta Josëwan Nicodemo säbanasman winapäcorgan. Winarcurnami Jesuspa ayanta pitupäcorgan pampananpag. 
\p  
\v 41 Jesusta crucificashgan naupanchömi cargan frütacuna plantarashgan juc huerta. Tsaychömi cargan pitapis manarag pampapäcushgan mushog sepultüra.  
\v 42 Sábado jamay junag galaycunanpagna captinmi tsay sepultüralamanna Jesusta pampapäcorgan. 
\c 20  
\s1 Wanushganpita Jesucristo cawarimushgan 
\r (Mateo 28.1-10; Marcos 16.1-8; Lucas 24.1-12) 
\p  
\v 1 Domingo tutami María Magdalena tsaca tsacala aywargan Jesús pamparaycashgan cagman. Tsayman chayarmi tarergan sepultüra tsaparag rumi wititsishga caycagta.  
\v 2 Tsayta ricaycurmi cörrila cutergan Jesús cuyashgan discïpulunta y Simón Pedruta wilananpag. Chayaycurnami paycunata caynog wilargan: “¡Jesuspa ayantami apacärishga! ¡Manami musyapäcötsu maypa apacärishgantapis!” 
\p  
\v 3-4 Tsaynog wilaptinmi Pedruwan Jesús cuyashgan discïpulun cörrila aywargan Jesús pamparashgan cagman. Pedruta yalirirmi puntata jucag discípulu chayargan.  
\v 5 Tsaychönami punculapita watgaycur ricargan säbanaslana caycagta.  
\v 6-7 Simón Pedrumi itsanga ruriman yaycorgan. Tsaychömi paypis säbanaslata tarergan. Jesuspa umanta watapashgan träputapis juc läducho churaraycagtami tarergan.  
\v 8 Tsaypitaragmi jucag discïpulunpis ruriman yaycur Jesús cawarimushganta criyergan.  
\v 9 Tsaynog caycaptinpis manami tantyapäcorganragtsu Tayta Diospa palabrancho cawarimunanpag escribiraycashganta.  
\v 10 Tsaypitanami discïpuluncuna cuticärergan posädarashgan wayiman. 
\s1 María Magdalenata Jesucristo yuripashgan 
\r (Marcos 16.9-11) 
\p  
\v 11-12 Marianami itsanga pamparashgan cagman cutiycur wagar puncucho quëdacorgan. Wagaycashgancho ruriman watgaycurmi ricargan ishcay angilcuna yorag röpashga caycagta. Jucag jamaraycargan Jesuspa uman cashgan cagcho y jucagnami jamaraycargan chaquin cashgan cagcho.  
\v 13 Tsay angilcunami Mariata taporgan caynog nir: “¿Imanirtag wagaycanqui?” 
\p Tsaynog tapuptin caynog nergan: “Jesuspa ayantami apacärishga, tayta. Manami musyätsu maypa apacärishgantapis.” 
\p  
\v 14 Tsaynog nir ticraycushganchömi Jesusta ricargan. Itsanga manami reguergantsu pay cashgantaga.  
\v 15 Tsaymi Jesús caynog taporgan: “¿Imanirtag wagaycanqui? ¿Pitatag ashiycanqui?” 
\p Tsauraga huertacho arog runa cashganta yarparmi María nergan: “Maymanpis Jesuspa ayanta apashga carga shuntacunäpag wilaycalämay, tayta.” 
\p  
\v 16 Tsauraga Jesús caynog nergan: “¡María!” 
\p Mariata jutinpa gayaptinmi tantyargan Jesús cashganta. Tsaymi “¡Raboni!” nergan. Raboni ninanga yachatsicog ninanmi. 
\p  
\v 17 Nircurmi Jesús nergan: “Ama tsarimaytsu. Manaragmi Taytä cagman cutishcäragtsu. Tsaypa trucanga ayway wilamuy discïpulöcunata Taytäman cuticunäpag cashganta. Paycunaga wauguëcunami caycan. Nogapa Taytäga gamcunapapis taytayquimi y Diosnëga gamcunapapis Diosniquimi.” 
\p  
\v 18 Tsaynog niptinmi María jucla aywargan Jesús yuripashganta y nishgancunatapis wilananpag. 
\s1 Discïpuluncunata Jesucristo yuripashgan 
\r (Mateo 28.16-20; Marcos 16.14-18; Lucas 24.36-49) 
\p  
\v 19 Jesús cawarimushgan tsacaymi discïpuluncuna juntacargan juc wayiman. Israel runacunapa autoridänincunata mantsacurmi puncuta trancacurcur carcaycargan. Tsaycho carcaycaptinmi elagpita paycunapa naupancho Jesús ricacorgan. Nircurnami saludargan caynog nir: “Tayta Diosnintsi yanapayculäshunqui ali cawanayquipag.” 
\p  
\v 20 Tsaynog nirmi maquinta y lapsha pachanta ricatsergan. Tsaymi Jesusta ricaycur discïpuluncuna pasaypa cushicärergan.  
\v 21 Tsaypitana Jesús yapay caynog nergan: “Tayta Diosnintsi yanapayculäshunqui ali cawanayquipag.” 
\p Nircurna nergan: “Taytä cachamashgannoglami gamcunatapis cachaycä wilacuynëta wilacärinayquipag.” 
\p  
\v 22 Tsaynog nishpanmi discïpuluncuna cagman pücashpan caynog nergan: “Santu Espirituta chasquipäcuy.  
\v 23 Cananpitaga nogata chasquicamagcunata tantyatsinqui jutsancunapita perdonashgana cashganta y mana chasquicamagcunataga wilanqui jutsancunapita mana perdonashga cashganta.” 
\s1 Jesucristo Tomaswan tincushgan 
\p  
\v 24 Discïpuluncuna juntaraycashgan cagman Jesús chayananpäga Milïshu nishgan Tomás manami tsaychötsu cargan.  
\v 25 Tomaswan tincurnami waquin cag discípulu mayincuna caynog wilapäcorgan: “¡Señornintsi Jesustami ricapäcushcä!” 
\p Tsauraga Tomás nergan: “¡Quevä! Rasunpa cawarimushganta criyinäpäga maquinman clävo yaycushgantaragmi ricäman y tsayman dëdötaragmi jatëman, tsaynogpis lapsha pachanpa tucsishgantaragmi yatäman.” 
\p  
\v 26 Tsaypita juc semänata discïpuluncuna yapay juntacargan juc wayiman. Tsaychömi itsanga Tomaspis caycargan. Tsaycho puncuta trancacurcur carcaycaptinmi Jesús paycunapa naupancho elagpita yurircur saludargan caynog nir: “¡Tayta Diosnintsi yanapayculäshunqui ali cawanayquipag!” 
\p  
\v 27 Nircurnami Tomasta nergan: “Tomás, maquëta ricay y clävo yaycushganman dëduyquita jatiy. Lapsha pachäpa tucsimashgantapis yatay. ¿Imanirtag cawarimushgäta mana criyinquitsu?” 
\p  
\v 28 Tsaynog niptinmi Tomás nergan: “¡Gamga Diosnëmi canqui, tayta!” 
\p  
\v 29 Jesusnami nergan: “¿Ricaycamarragcu criyinqui? ¡Mana ricaycämarpis cawarimushgäta criyegcunaga cushishgami cangapag!” 
\s1 Cay libruta Juan imapag escribishganpis 
\p  
\v 30 Atsca milagrucunatami Jesús rurargan discïpuluncuna ricaycaptin. Tsaycunaga manami lapantsu cay librucho escribiraycan.  
\v 31 Cay librucho cagcunaga escribiraycan Jesusga salvamagnintsi Cristo cashganta y Diospa tsurin cashganta criyipäcunayquipagmi. Tsaymi payta chasquicorga gloriacho cushishgala imayyagpis cawapäcunquipag. 
\c 21  
\s1 Ganchis discïpuluncunata Jesucristo yuripashgan 
\p  
\v 1 Tsaypitanami Tiberias\f + \fr 21:1 \ft Tiberias nishgan lagünaga Galilea lagünami caycan.\f* nishgan lagüna cuchuncho Jesús yapay discïpuluncunata yuripargan.  
\v 2 Tsay lagüna cuchunchömi caycargan Simón Pedro, Milïshu nishgan Tomás y Natanaelpis. Natanaelga cargan Galilea provinciacho Caná marcapitami. Zebedeupa ishcan tsurincuna más ishcay discípulu mayincunapis tsaychömi carcaycargan.  
\v 3 Tsaymi Simón Pedro caynog nergan: “Pescädo tsaregmi aywaycä.” 
\p Tsaynog niptinmi discípulu mayincuna nergan: “Nogacunatapis yanapanäpag pushaycalämay.” 
\p Tsauraga büquiman witsarcur lapan aywargan. Tsay tsacay waraylata pescacuycarpis manami ni juc pescädulatapis tsaripäcorgantsu.  
\v 4 Patsa waraycaptinnami discïpulucuna ricargan juc runa lagüna cuchuncho caycagta. Itsanga manami musyapäcorgantsu Jesús cashganta.  
\v 5 Paymi caynog gayacorgan: “¿Naganacu pescäduta tsaripäcushcanqui?” 
\p Tsauraga discïpulucuna caynog nergan: “Manami ni juclaylatapis tsaripäcöragtsu, tayta.” 
\p  
\v 6 Tsaymi Jesús discïpulucunata caynog nergan: “Redniquita mashtapäcuy büquipa derëcha cag lädunman. Tsaypitami pescäduta tsaripäcamunquipag.” 
\p Nishgannog redta mashtarnami tsaripäcorgan tsaytsica pescäduta, hasta tsutaytapis mana puëdishganyag.  
\v 7 Tsauraga cuyashgan cag discïpulun Jesús cashganta reguiycur Pedruta caynog nergan: “¡Payga Jesusmi!” 
\p Tsaynog niptinmi jorgushgan cag röpanta jaticurcur Simón Pedro jucla Jesús cagman nadyaypa aywargan.  
\v 8 Waquin cag discïpuluncunami itsanga büquiwan aywapäcorgan. Lagüna cuchunpita pachac (100) metrunogla captinmi red junta pescäduta yacu cuchunman garachapäcorgan.  
\v 9 Tsayman chayarnami redta cachaycur büquipita yargapäcorgan. Tsaychömi taripäcorgan shansha janancho pescädo cancashga caycagta y tantatapis. 
\p  
\v 10 Tsauraga Jesús caynog nergan: “Tsay tsaripäcamushgayqui pescäduta juc ishcayta apamuy cancanantsipag.” 
\p  
\v 11 Tsaynog niptinmi Simón Pedro büquiman witsarcur redta garachamorgan pescäducunata shuntapäcunanpag. Tsay redchöga cargan pachac pitsga chunca quimsa (153) jatusag pescäducunami. Tsaytsica pescädo caycaptinpis red manami rachergantsu.  
\v 12 Tsauraga Jesús nergan: “Micunantsipag shapäcamuyna.” 
\p Jesús cashganta musyarmi maygan discïpulunpis mana tapupargantsu pï cashgantapis.  
\v 13 Jesús cashgan cagman chayaptinnami tantata y pescäduta paycunata ayporgan. 
\p  
\v 14 Tsaywanga quimsa cutinami discïpuluncunata Jesús yuripargan. 
\s1 Simón Pedruwan Jesucristo parlashgan 
\p  
\v 15 Micuyta usharcurnami Jesús taporgan Simón Pedruta caynog nir: “Jonaspa tsurin Pedro, ¿lapanpitapis mascu gam cuyamanqui?” 
\p Tsaynog tapuptin Pedro nergan: “Au tayta, gam musyanquimi cuyashgäta.” 
\p Tsauraga Jesús nergan: “Tsaynog carga mitsicog runa uyshancunata ricashgannog nogaman yäracamagcunata shumag ricanqui.” 
\p  
\v 16 Jesús yapay taporgan Simón Pedruta: “Jonaspa tsurin Simón, ¿gam cuyamanquicu?” 
\p Tsaynog tapuptin Pedro nergan: “Au tayta, gam musyanquimi cuyashgäta.” 
\p Niptinmi nergan: “Tsaynog carga mitsicog runa uyshancunata ricashgannog nogaman yäracamagcunata shumag ricanqui.” 
\p  
\v 17 Tsaypita Jesús yapay taporgan Simón Pedruta: “Jonaspa tsurin Simón, ¿gam rasunpacu cuyamanqui?” 
\p Quimsa cuti Jesús tsaynogla tapuptinmi Pedro laquishga nergan: “Gam lapantapis musyanquimi, tayta. Tsaynogpis musyanquimi gamta cuyashgäta.” 
\p Niptinmi Jesús nergan: “Tsauraga mitsicog runa uyshancunata ricashgannog nogaman yäracamagcunata shumag ricanqui.  
\v 18 Mözularag carga quiquilayquimi röpayquita jaticorgayqui maypapis munashgayquipa aywanayquipag. Auquinna captiquinami itsanga ricrayquita mashtarcuptiqui jucna röpayquita jatipäshunquipag. Tsaynogpis aywayta mana munashgayquipami apashunquipag.” 
\p  
\v 19 Tsaynog nirmi Jesús tantyatsergan payman yäracushganpita Pedro crucificaypa wanutsishga cananpag cashganta. Nircurnami Pedruta caynog nergan: “Nishgäcunata imaypis cumpliy.” 
\s1 Libro ushanan 
\p  
\v 20-21 Tsaypitanami Pedro ticrarcamur Jesús cuyashgan cag discïpulunta ricargan pay cagman aywaycagta. Payta ricärirmi Jesusta caynog taporgan: “Tayta, paytaga ¿imatag pasanga?” 
\p (Manarag Jesús wanuptinmi cuyashgan discïpulun naupalancho micorgan. Tsaychömi payta taporgan maygan discïpulun contran sharcunanpag cashgantapis.) 
\p  
\v 22 Pedro tsaynog tapuptinmi Jesús nergan: “¿Imanirtag paypag tapuycämanqui? Cutimunäyag cawanan captinpis gamga nishgäcunata lapanta cumpliy.” 
\p  
\v 23 Tsaynog niptinmi waquin discïpulucuna yarpapäcorgan tsay cuyashgan discïpulun imaypis mana wanunanpag cashganta. Tsaynog yarpapäcuptinpis Jesusga manami mana wanunanpag cashgantatsu nergan, sinöga: “Cutimunäyag cawanan captinpis ¿imanirtag paypag tapuycämanqui?” nergan. 
\p  
\v 24 Jesuspa cuyashgan discïpulun carmi caycunata escribishcä. Lapan escribishgäcunaga rasun caglami caycan.  
\v 25 Jesús rurashgancunaga cay escribishgäcunapitapis masragmi caycan. Lapan rurashgancunata escriberga manami imaypis ushämantsu cargan. [Amén.]